MIFCI310(mi) 
    S mi=$G(mi) 
    Q:'$L(mi)
  
	s par11=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),12) 		//项目分隔符
	s par10=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),13) 	//结果分隔符
	s AntDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),14) 		//抗生素分隔符
	s SenDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),15) 		//药敏结果分隔符
	s par4="|TCP|"_$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),17)  	//端口号

	S mi1=mi
    S stx=$C(2),etx=$C(3),ack=$C(6),enq=$C(5),eot=$C(4),etb=$C(23)
    S sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)  
    S lf=$C(10),nak=$C(21),(AllRecord,result,epis)="",kk=1
    
    S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,errFlag,resultType)=""
    Q:$$StartUTF8^MI.MIF000(mi)
	F {
		D Main
		Q:$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
	}
    C par4
    Q
    
Main 
    S $ZT="ErrHandler",$EC=""
    R *R:10
	Q:'$TEST	//如果超时则退出
	Q:$c(R)'=sb   //以sb开头
	S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,errFlag,resultType,msgType,barcode,mshStr)=""
	S startTime=$P($H,",",2)
	K PLIST
	S index=1
	k ^TMIFLIS(mi,"Record")
	F {
		S curTime=$P($H,",",2)
		Q:curTime>(startTime+300)  //5分钟内没有处理完则退出循环
		Q:$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
		R *R:10
		Q:'$TEST	//如果超时则退出
	
		;s indexQ=$o(^TMIFLIS(mi,"Record",""),-1)+1,^TMIFLIS(mi,"Record",indexQ)=$c(R)
		I $L($G(PLIST(index)))>=32700 {  //32767
			S index=+$O(PLIST(""),-1)+1
			S PLIST(index)=""
		}
		I $C(R)'=eb,$C(R)'=cr {
			S PLIST(index)=$G(PLIST(index))_$C(R)
			
		}
		I ($C(R)=eb)||($c(R)=cr) {  	//解析一条记录
			D Record
			K PLIST
			S index=1	
		}	
		Q:$C(R)=eb   	//循环读取,当为eb的时候则退出
	}
	i $L(epis),$L(result) D Save
	Q
	
Record
    S index=""
    S segmentType="",dataTye="",graphType="",base64Stream=""
    S isImage=0,isBinary=0
    F {
		S index=$O(PLIST(index))
		Q:'$L(index)
		S record=$TR($G(PLIST(index)),cr)
		Continue:'$L(record)
		i record["Connect" /*D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"Q","Q<--M")*/ s index="" q
		D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"H<--M")	
		I index=1 {
			S segmentType=$P(record,"|",1)
			I segmentType="MSH" {	//信息头信息
				S mshStr=record
				//消息类型
    			S msgType=$P($P(record,"|",9),"^",1)  //ORU,ACK,QRY,QCK,DSR	
    			S msgReq=$P(record,"|",10) 	
    			I msgType="ORU" {
	    			D SendACK(mi,record,"AA",0,"Message accepted")
	    		}
	    		I msgType="ORM" {
	    		}
	    		S resultType=$P(record,"|",11)
			}
			
			I segmentType="PID" {	//患者信息
				S epis=$P(record,"|",3) 	
			}
			
			I segmentType="PVI" {	//就诊信息
					
			}
			
			I segmentType="OBR" {	//医嘱信息
				i '$l(epis) S epis=$P(record,"|",3) 
    			i '$l(epis) s epis=$P(record,"|",4)
    			S dateStr=$P(record,"|",8)
     			I dateStr?14N {
	     			//S date=$ZDH($E(dateStr,1,4)_"-"_$E(dateStr,5,6)_"-"_$E(dateStr,7,8),3)
	     			//S time=$ZTH($E(dateStr,9,10)_":"_$E(dateStr,11,12)_":"_$E(dateStr,13,14),1)	
	     		}
			}
			
			I segmentType="OBX" {
				S dataTye=$P(record,"|",3)  //NM (numeric) 表示数字值，用于定量项目,
     										//ST (string) 表示字符串值，用于定性项目
    			S channel=$P(record,"|",4)
    			S value=$P(channel,"^",1)
    			S channel=$tr($P(channel,"^",4)," ")
				i $l(channel),$l(value) s result=result_channel_par10_value_par11
			}
			
			I segmentType="QRD" {	//双向查询
				S barcode=$P(record,"|",9)
				I $L(barcode) {  //双向
					D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,barcode,"barcode")
					d SendQRD(mi,record_"^"_msgReq,barcode)
					
				}
			}	
		}
    }
    Q
  
 
Save  
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"^"_result,"Result")	
  	I $l(epis),$l(result) {
	  	S QC=""
  		D Save^MI.MIF000(mi,epis,result,date,time,QC)
  	}
  	S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,resultType)=""
  	Q
  
SendACK(mi,mshStr,ackType="AA",errCode=0,errDesc="Message accepted") //send 'ack' to instrument 
    N (mi,mshStr,ackType,errCode,errDesc)
    S mi=$g(mi),mshStr=$g(mshStr),ackType=$g(ackType),errCode=$g(errCode),errDesc=$g(errDesc)
    S ret=1,sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)
    Q:('$l(mi))||('$l(mshStr)) ret
    S mshStr=$TR(mshStr,cr,"")
    //Q:$l(mshStr,"|")<21 ret
    S ret=0
    S msgRoutine=$P($P(mshStr,"|",9),"^",2)
    S seq=$P(mshStr,"|",10)
    S mshStr=$P(mshStr,"|",1,2)_"|LIS|||"_$P(mshStr,"|",6,$l(mshStr))
    
    S $P(mshStr,"|",9)="ACK^"_msgRoutine
    W sb,mshStr,cr,"MSA|"_ackType_"|"_seq_"|"_errDesc_"|||"_errCode_"|",cr,eb,cr,*-3
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$S(ackType="AA":"ACK",ackType="AE":"Error",ackType="AR":"NAK",1:"NULL"),"H-->M")
    Q ret
    
ErrHandler
	D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$TR($ZERROR,"^","--")_".错误代码:"_$ECODE,"Runtime Error")
    Q 



SendQRD(mi,record,labno)
	N (mi,record,AckType,ErrCode,ErrDesc,mshStr,labno)
	s mi=$g(mi),record=$g(record),AckType=$g(AckType),ErrCode=$g(ErrCode),ErrDesc=$g(ErrDesc),mshStr=$g(mshStr),labno=$g(labno)
	S ret=1,sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)
	Q:('$l(mi))||('$l(record))
    s msgReq=$p(record,"^",2)
    s record=$p(record,"^",1)
	d ScanOne^MI.MIF000(mi,labno) ;创建上传化验项目列表
	S date=$tr($zd(+$h,3),"-")
	S time=$tr($zt($p($h,",",2)),":")
	///无对应样本，则返回消息为
	s MSH="MSH|^~\&|Automatis CoagulationAnalyzer|Ci-300|Lis|Lis|"_date_time_"||QCK^Q02|"_msgReq_"|P|2.3.1||||||UTF-8"_cr
	s MSA="MSA|AA"_cr
	s ERR="ERR|0|"_cr
	i '$D(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,labno)) {
		s QAK="QAK|SR|NF|"_cr
		s mshStr=MSH_MSA_QAK
		w sb,mshStr,eb,cr,*-3
		D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,sb_mshStr_eb_cr,"H->M-Q02")
		q
	}
	
	//返回QCK^Q02消息作应答
	s QAK="QAK|SR|OK|"_cr
	s mshStr=MSH_MSA_QAK
	w sb,mshStr,eb,cr,*-3
	D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,sb_mshStr_eb_cr,"H->M")
	//h 1     500ms内要发送项目信息
	

	//返回查询应答QCK^Q02消息后,再发送医嘱数据消息DSR^Q03
	s MSH="MSH|^~\&|Automatis CoagulationAnalyzer|Ci-300|Lis|Lis|"_date_time_"||DSR^Q03|"_msgReq_"|P|2.3.1||||||UTF-8"_cr
	s MSA="MSA|AA"_cr
	s QAK="QAK|SR|OK|||||"_cr
	s QRD="QRD|"_date_time_"|R|D|1|||RD|"_labno_"|OTH|||T"_cr
	s QRF="QRF||||||RCT|COR|ALL"_cr
	s VisitNumberDR = $o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno),""))
	//标本信息
	s RPVisitNumberData=$g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(VisitNumberDR))
	s RegNo=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,3)
	s BedNo=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,27)
	s SurName=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,13)
	s Age=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,18)
	s SpeciesDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,15),Species=""
	i $l(SpeciesDR) s Species=$lg($g(^dbo.BTSpeciesD(SpeciesDR)),3)
	s DoctorDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,23),Doctor=""
	i $l(DoctorDR) s Doctor=$lg($g(^dbo.BTDoctorD(DoctorDR)),3)
	s LocationDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,22),Location=""
	i $l(LocationDR) s Location=$lg($g(^dbo.BTLocationD(LocationDR)),3)
	s EpisNo=""
	s EpisNo=$$GetEpisNo(mi,labno)
	k DSP
	s DSP(1)="DSP|1||"_RegNo_cr
	s DSP(2)="DSP|2||"_BedNo_cr
	s DSP(3)="DSP|3||"_SurName_cr
	s DSP(4)="DSP|4||"_Age_cr
	s DSP(5)="DSP|5||"_Species_cr
	s DSP(6)="DSP|6||"_cr
	s DSP(7)="DSP|7"_cr
	s DSP(8)="DSP|8"_cr
	s DSP(9)="DSP|9"_cr
	s DSP(10)="DSP|10"_cr
	s DSP(11)="DSP|11||"_cr
	s DSP(12)="DSP|12||"_cr
	s DSP(13)="DSP|13"_cr
	s DSP(14)="DSP|14"_cr
	s DSP(15)="DSP|15||"_cr
	s DSP(16)="DSP|16"_cr
	s DSP(17)="DSP|17||"_cr
	s DSP(18)="DSP|18"_cr
	s DSP(19)="DSP|19"_cr
	s DSP(20)="DSP|20||"_cr
	s DSP(21)="DSP|21||"_labno_cr
	s DSP(22)="DSP|22||"_EpisNo_cr
	s DSP(23)="DSP|23||"_cr
	s DSP(24)="DSP|24||"_cr
	s DSP(25)="DSP|25||"_cr
	s DSP(26)="DSP|26||"_cr
	s DSP(27)="DSP|27||"_Doctor_cr
	s DSP(28)="DSP|28||"_Location_cr
	s seq=29
	S chl="" F  S chl=$o(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,labno,chl)) Q:chl=""  D
	.s DSP(seq)="DSP|"_seq_"||"_chl_cr
	.s seq=seq+1
	
	s DSPs=""
	s seq="" f  s seq=$o(DSP(seq)) q:seq=""  d
	.s DSPs=DSPs_DSP(seq)
	s DSC="DSC|0"_cr
	s mshStr=MSH_MSA_ERR_QAK_QRD_QRF_DSPs_DSC
	w sb,mshStr,eb,cr,*-3
	D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,sb_mshStr_eb_cr,"H->M")
	Q
///zw $$GetEpisNo^MI.MIFKUF40B("38","25062308821")
GetEpisNo(mi,labno)
	s ret="",mi=$g(mi),labno=$g(labno)
	i '$l(mi) q labno
	s WGMachineID=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6)
	i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",labno)) d
	.s VisitnumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",labno,""))
	.i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitnumberDR,WGMachineID,1)) d
	..s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitnumberDR,WGMachineID,1,""))
	..s ret=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(ReportDR)),8)
	q ret

	S mi=$g(mi) i '$l(mi) q
	Q:'$D(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi))
	S par4=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),10)
	S par9=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),11)
	S par11=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),12) 
	S par10=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),13)
	S:$L(par10) par10=$ASCII(par10)
	S:$L(par11) par11=$ASCII(par11)
	s stx=$c(2),etx=$c(3),ack=$c(6),enq=$c(5),eot=$c(4),etb=$c(23)
	s lf=$c(10),cr=$c(13),nak=$c(21)
	s (AllRecord,result,epis)=""
	SET $ZTRAP="ErrHandler",$EC=""
	
	Q:$$StartUTF8^MI.MIF000(mi)
	s par4="|TCP|"_$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),10)  	//端口号
	s IP=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),9)
	s Port=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),10)
	s LinkTime=0
	s Device="|TCP|"_Port
	F {
		try{
			;d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$ZA,"ZA")
			//未启动客户端/服务端0，客户端断开连接标志20484，无客户端连接20480，有客户端连接28674，连接并建立数据传输28672
			//lis断开
			i $ZA="0" {
				h 2
				open Device:(IP:Port:/IOTABLE="UTF8"):20
				use Device
				d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"lis断开连接"_$zd($p($h,",",1),3)_" "_$zt($p($h,",",2)),"lisReConnect")
				//throw ##class(%Exception.General).%New("ConnectError","D",,"重新连接失败")
				}
			//仪器断开，或者无数据1min，重启tcp
			;i (($ZA="20484")||(LinkTime=6)) {
			i (($ZA="20484")) {
				close par4
				d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"仪器断开连接"_$zd($p($h,",",1),3)_" "_$zt($p($h,",",2)),"blockConnect")
				h 2
				open Device:(IP:Port:/IOTABLE="UTF8"):20
				use Device
				d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"重新连接"_$zd($p($h,",",1),3)_" "_$zt($p($h,",",2)),"reConnect")
				s LinkTime=0
				continue
				}
			//连接无数据传输，main每执行6次，即1min，重启tcp
			i $ZA="28674" s LinkTime=$i(LinkTime)
			//正常传输了，就清空计数
			i $ZA="28672" s LinkTime=0
			d Main
	 	}catch ex{
		 s exception="错误:"_ex.Location_"^"_ex.Data_ex.Name
		 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,exception,"读取或写入异常，重启服务端")
	 	}
		Q:$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
	}
    C par4
    Q
    
	/*
	i $$StartUTF8^MI.MIF000(mi) q
	f  d Main i $$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi) q
	c par4
	q
	*/
ErrHandler
    h 10
    d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$tr($ZERROR,"^","--")_".错误代码:"_$ECODE,"Runtime Error")
    q
Main
	s (AllRecord,chl,res,epis,episRecord,result,resultStr,mshStr,barcode,date,time,QC) = ""
	s record=$$Read^MI.MIF000(mi,$c(11),$c(28),"","",2) q:'$l(record)
	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"record<--M")
	d Result
	q

Result
	f irec=1:1:$l(record,$c(13)) {
		s resultStr=$p(record,$c(13),irec)
		d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,resultStr,"resultStr")
		q:resultStr=""
		s headType=$p(resultStr,"|",1)
		i headType="MSH" {
			s mshStr=resultStr
			s msgRoutine=$p($p(resultStr,"|",9),"^",1)
			i msgRoutine="ORU" {
				D SendACK(mi,resultStr,"AA",0,"Message accepted")
			}
		}
		//QRD|20210818151949|R|D|1|||RD|9230883|OTH|||T|QRF|F3999|20210818151949|20210818151949|||RCT|COR|ALL||
		I headType="QRD" {
			s barcode=$p(resultStr,"|",9)
			d SendDSR(mi,resultStr,"AA",0,"Message accepted",mshStr,barcode)
		}
		I headType="QRF" {
			//h 0.5
			//d SendDSR(mi,resultStr,"AA",0,"Message accepted",mshStr,barcode)
		}
		i headType="OBR" {
			S epis=$P(resultStr,"|",3) 
    		S:'$l(epis) epis=$P(resultStr,"|",4)
		}
		i headType="OBX" {
			S dataType=$P(resultStr,"|",3) //NM (numeric) 表示数字值，用于定量项目,
     										//ST (string) 表示字符串值，用于定性项目
			s chl=$TR($p($p(resultStr,"|",4),"^",2)," ")
			s chl=$tr(chl,"\","")
			s res=$p(resultStr,"|",6)
			I $L(chl),dataType'="ED",dataType'="IS" {
	    		s result=result_chl_$c(92)_res_$c(44)
    		}
    		
    		i dataType="IS"{
	    		s policeInfo=$TR($p($p(resultStr,"|",4),"^",1)," ")
	    		try{d ##Class(MI.Special.Common).SaveAlarmInformation(mi,epis,policeInfo,"DMD7")}catch{}	//保存报警信息
    		}
    		
    		I dataType="ED" {
	    		
	    		S graphType=chl
	    		S graphData=$P(res,"^",5)
    			S graphDataType=$P(res,"^",4)
    			I $ZCVT(graphDataType,"U")=$ZCVT("Base64","U") {
	    			D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,graphData,graphType)
	    			i graphType["RBCHistogram" d
	    			.//s ^LISDrawImageTask($h,mi,epis_"RBC")=$lb(epis,graphData,mi,"MI.MIFLISMonitorTest","-1","Histogram#RBC#RBC######10#10#320#138","LIS.Mach.ImageDeal.Imagebc6800,LIS.Mach.ImageDeal")
	    			.s tretObj=##Class(wbsLisMsgAsyncHandler.LISMsg.wbsLisDrawImageAsyncHandlerSoap).%New()
					.s tret=tretObj.DrawImage(epis,graphData,mi,"MI.MIFLISMonitorTest","-1","DiffPlot#RBC#RBC######10#10#320#138","LIS.Mach.ImageDeal.Imagebc6800,LIS.Mach.ImageDeal") 
	    			.D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,tret_"!"_$lb(epis,mi),"绘图："_graphType)
	    			i graphType["PLTHistogram" d
	    			.//s ^LISDrawImageTask($h,mi,epis_"PLT")=$lb(epis,graphData,mi,"MI.MIFLISMonitorTest","-1","Histogram#PLT#PLT######10#10#320#138","LIS.Mach.ImageDeal.Imagebc6800,LIS.Mach.ImageDeal")
	    			.s tretObj=##Class(wbsLisMsgAsyncHandler.LISMsg.wbsLisDrawImageAsyncHandlerSoap).%New()
					.s tret=tretObj.DrawImage(epis,graphData,mi,"MI.MIFLISMonitorTest","-1","DiffPlot#PLT#RBC######10#10#320#138","LIS.Mach.ImageDeal.Imagebc6800,LIS.Mach.ImageDeal") 
	    			.D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,tret_"!"_$lb(epis,mi),"绘图："_graphType)
	    			i graphType["NRBCScattergram" d
	    			.//s OldgraphDataDIFF=graphData
					.//s ^LISDrawImageTask($h,mi,epis_"WBC-DIFF")=$lb(epis,graphData,mi,"MI.MIFLISMonitorTest","-1","DiffPlot#DIFF#######10#10#320#138","LIS.Mach.ImageDeal.Imagebc6800,LIS.Mach.ImageDeal")
					.s tretObj=##Class(wbsLisMsgAsyncHandler.LISMsg.wbsLisDrawImageAsyncHandlerSoap).%New()
					.s tret=tretObj.DrawImage(epis,graphData,mi,"MI.MIFLISMonitorTest","-1","DiffPlot#DIFF#######10#10#320#138","LIS.Mach.ImageDeal.Imagebc6800,LIS.Mach.ImageDeal") 
	    			.D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,tret_"!"_$lb(epis,mi),"绘图："_graphType)
	    			i graphType["WBCDIFFScattergram" d
	    			.//s ^LISDrawImageTask($h,mi,epis_"BASO")=$lb(epis,graphData,mi,"MI.MIFLISMonitorTest","-1","DiffPlot#WNB#######10#10#320#138","LIS.Mach.ImageDeal.Imagebc6800,LIS.Mach.ImageDeal")
    				.s tretObj=##Class(wbsLisMsgAsyncHandler.LISMsg.wbsLisDrawImageAsyncHandlerSoap).%New()
					.s tret=tretObj.DrawImage(epis,graphData,mi,"MI.MIFLISMonitorTest","-1","DiffPlot#Baso#######10#10#320#138","LIS.Mach.ImageDeal.Imagebc6800,LIS.Mach.ImageDeal") 
    				.D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,tret_"!"_$lb(epis,mi),"绘图："_graphType)
    			}
    		}
			
		}
		i headType="ORC" {
			S barcode=$P(resultStr,"|",4)
			//S:$ZCVT(barcode,"U")=$ZCVT("Invalid","U") barcode="" //条码扫描错误
			//I $L(barcode) { //双向 
			//} Invalid 条码扫描错误
			d SendORR(mi,resultStr,"AA",0,"Message accepted",mshStr,barcode)
		}
	}
	d Last
	q
  
Last 
	// 保存结果
	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"$$"_result,"Result")
	i $l(epis),$l(result) d Save^MI.MIF000(mi,epis,result,date,time,QC) 
	s (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC)=""
	q

///*****************************拼装应答信息************************************///
SendACK(mi,mshStr,ackType="AA",errCode=0,errDesc="Message accepted") //send 'ack' to instrument 
	N (mi,mshStr,ackType,errCode,errDesc)
	S mi=$g(mi),mshStr=$g(mshStr),ackType=$g(ackType),errCode=$g(errCode),errDesc=$g(errDesc)
	S ret=1,sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)
	Q:('$l(mi))||('$l(mshStr)) ret
	S mshStr=$TR(mshStr,cr,"")
	S ret=0
	S msgRoutine=$P($P(mshStr,"|",9),"^",2)
	S seq=$P(mshStr,"|",10)
	s msaStr="MSA|"_ackType_"|"_seq_"|"_errDesc_"|||"_errCode_"|"
	D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,msaStr,"H-->M")
	W sb,msaStr,eb,cr,*-3
	//D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,msaStr,"H-->M")
	Q ret

			"DSP|5||"_"WH_BLOOD"_"||"

SearchTestItemOther(mi,epis)
	S tcx="",tc="",Num=29,TcNum=0
	d ScanOne^MI.MIF000(mi,epis)
  	i $d(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,epis)){
	   f {
	 	s tc=$o(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,epis,tc))
	 	 q:tc=""
    	i tcx="" s tcx=tc
    	e  i tcx'="" s tcx=tcx_"+"_tc
    	s TcNum=TcNum+1
    	s Num=Num+1
  	}
  	}
  	D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,tcx_"@"_TcNum,"H->M3")
    Q tcx 
	
SearchTestItem(mi,epis)
	// 拼装通道号信息
    S tcx="",tc="",Num=6,TcNum=0

			s tcx=tcx_"DSP|"_Num_"||"_tc_"||"_cr
			s TcNum=TcNum+1
			s Num=Num+1
	 	 }

    Q tcx_"@"_TcNum
    
///*****************************获取信息************************************///
GetPatInfo(labno,mi)
	/// 病人信息
	/// d GetPatInfo^MI.MIFQ29N("9000000248","11")
    s labno = $g(labno),mi=$g(mi)
	i $l(labno)=0 q ""
	s VisitNumberDR = $o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno),""))
	i '$l(VisitNumberDR) q ""
	s RPVisitNumberData=$g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(VisitNumberDR))
	s LocationDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,22),Location=""
	i $l(LocationDR) s Location=$lg($g(^dbo.BTLocationD(LocationDR)),3)
	s DoctorDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,23),Doctor=""
	i $l(DoctorDR) s Doctor=$lg($g(^dbo.BTDoctorD(DoctorDR)),3)
	s ReceiveDate=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,66)
	s ReceiveTime=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,67)
	s ReceiveUserDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,68),ReceiveUser=""
	i $l(ReceiveUserDR) s ReceiveUser=$lg($g(^dbo.SYSUserD(ReceiveUserDR)),3)
	s RegNo=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,3)
	s SurName=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,13)
 	s GivenName=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,14)
	i SurName=GivenName s PatName=SurName
	e  s PatName=SurName_GivenName	
	s SpeciesDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,15),Species=""
	i $l(SpeciesDR) s Species=$lg($g(^dbo.BTSpeciesD(SpeciesDR)),3)
	s AdmTypeDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,4),AdmType=""
	i $l(AdmTypeDR) s AdmType=$lg($g(^dbo.BTAdmissionTypeD(AdmTypeDR)),2)
	s BedNo=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,27)
	s Age=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,18)
	s BirthDate=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,16)
	s AgeUnitDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,19),AgeUnit=""
	i $l(AgeUnitDR) s AgeUnit=$lg($g(^dbo.BTAgeUnitD(AgeUnitDR)),3)
	s CollectDate=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,51)
	s CollectTime=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,52)
	s Diagnose=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,28)

接口说明

仪器厂商 东芝TBA-FX8
 仪器型号 东芝TBA-FX8
通讯方式 单向|双向☑|主动上传
 仪器类型 生化
医院名称
程序名称
终端服务器地址 终端服务器端口号

仪器上接口标示和接口类型

  1. 接口类型：串口☑|网口|监听文件|数据库|其他
  2. 连接方式：HL7协议|ASTM协议|监听文件|数据库|其他☑

仪器接口说明

  • 仪器连接说明 https://file6d66f4de2a95.vrh5.cn/v3/idea/YnWDdZ8i?suid=7CBF7E3A-ECBC-4D30-8B49-03C69FF065C3&sl=1

  • 仪器回复一定要回复【2】【6】【3】，单纯回复【6】，仪器会识别不到，造成传输结果过慢

  • 仪器设置为双向后无法单向，质控以及定标，本院为仪器厂商到现场固定架子号位置，固定做单向质控

串口盒子配置

  • 波特率： 9600
  • 数据位：8
  • 停止位： 1
  • 校验位： N

仪器图片

仪器配置

点击下侧中间小电脑，再点击config即可查看配置

双向配置切换

初始界面右下角Run按钮，随后点击System

传结果位置

点击右侧第三个按钮Online，弹窗后点击左侧第三个Send 即可发送

Class MI.MIFSLAN96P Extends %RegisteredObject
{

// ==================配置====================//

/// 标题
Parameter Data = "反应孔~项目~样本名称~管号~管名~通道~染料~目标~颜色~类型~属性~复管编号~Ct~平均Ct~Ct SD~Ct CV(%)~浓度~平均浓度~Cn SD ~Cn CV (%)~Rn~目标结论~管结论~样本结论~唯一标识";

/// 流水号
Parameter Epis = "唯一标识";

/// 通道号
Parameter Code = "目标";

/// 结果
Parameter Res = "浓度";

/// 扩展结果
Parameter Res1;

// ==================配置====================//

/// [{"MachID":"#RowID","Type":"Drect","UpTime":"3000","Address":"D:\\LISDATA\\","UpCDF":"","UpREF":"","DealProcess":"MI.MIFSLAN96P","Para":".csv","PreDealClass":"PreDeal.DealDemoMAll,PreDeal","UPPreDealClass":""}]
/// 分隔符:~
/// mi:仪器主键
/// record:一个数据行合并提交用#enter#分割多行数据
/// epis:流水号，前处理提取出了的画
/// fileNameOrColName:读文件的是文件全名，数据库的是数据库查询的列名用~分割
/// d ##class(MI.MIFAGS4800).fileMTHD("33","试管号~检测流水号~样本名称~样本ID~FAM 标准浓度~FAM 计算浓度~FAM 对数浓度~FAM Ct值~FAM 结果~VIC 标准浓度~VIC 计算浓度~VIC 对数浓度~VIC Ct值~VIC 结果~姓名~性别~年龄~科室~病室~床~住院号~诊断~标本类型~检验~标本性状~检测项目~单位~送检者~代码~检验者~审核者~送检日期~报告日期~NO[13][10]A01~2.02211E+15~CT~1~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~")
/// d ##class(MI.MIFSLAN96P).fileMTHD("241","A1~HBV-SX~~1~管1~1~FAM~HBV~#FF0013FF~待测样品~~~NoCt~~~~<1.000E2~~~~0.003~~~~00001~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~0.00891~0.00777~0.00654~0.00518~0.00384~0.00267~0.00168~0.00086~0.00015~-0.00048~-0.00100~-0.00136~-0.00162~-0.00182~-0.00196~-0.00197~-0.00185~-0.00165~-0.00141~-0.00106~-0.00062~-0.00023~-0.00003~0.00008~0.00022~0.00032~0.00026~0.00011~0.00001~-0.00004~-0.00006~-0.00010~-0.00018~-0.00028~-0.00025~-0.00006~0.00017~0.00030~0.00042~0.00071~0.00116~0.00166~0.00209~0.00244~0.00271~~5185.68~5179.31~5171.61~5162.58~5155.14~5147.71~5140.88~5134.62~5129.34~5123.42~5118.42~5113.74~5110.04~5105.78~5101.99~5098.61~5096.05~5093.34~5090.94~5088.84~5086.72~5085.99~5082.81~5079.12~5077.52~5074.07~5071.06~5066.50~5063.24~5060.21~5056.18~5053.24~5049.67~5046.31~5041.92~5040.60~5038.06~5034.90~5032.10~5029.50~5028.56~5026.65~5024.89~5023.17~5020.51")
ClassMethod fileMTHD(mi, record As %String(MAXLEN=99999999), epis, fileNameOrColName, P4, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %String
{
	s mi=$g(mi)
    i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q
    s (sample,epis,result,date,time,QC)=""
    i '$l(record) q
    d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"H<--M")
	s Deli="~" //结果分隔符
	s RDdli="," //通道号分隔符
	s ResultDeli=$c(92) //结果分隔符 
	s ItemDeli=$c(44) //项目分隔符
	
	
	s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Data")=..#Data
	s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Code","Epis")=..#Epis
	s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Code","Code")=..#Code
	s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Code","Res")=..#Res
	s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Code","Res1")=..#Res1
	
	s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Epis")=""
	s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Code")=""
	s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Res")=""
	s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Res1")=""
	
	//单项目
	for i=1:1:$l(record,"[13][10]") d
	.s rec=$p(record,"[13][10]",i)
	.d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,rec,"rec")
	.d ResultInfo(rec)
	k ^LISMachineEpis(mi)
    q ""
    
    
ResultInfo(rec)
	i rec[..#Epis d ResultInfoTitle(rec)		//标题头行获取
	e  d
	.i '$l($g(^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Epis"))) d
	..d ResultInfoTitleNew		//初始化位置，获取所需列数字
	..d ResultInfoData(rec)
	.e  d ResultInfoData(rec)
	q
	
ResultInfoData(rec)
	s EpisNum=$g(^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Epis"))
	s CodeNum=$g(^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Code"))
	s ResNum=$g(^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Res"))
	s Res1Num=$g(^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Res1"))
	s epis=$p(rec,Deli,EpisNum)
	i $l(epis) s epis=+epis
	s code=$p(rec,Deli,CodeNum)
	s res=$p(rec,Deli,ResNum)
	s res1=$p(rec,Deli,Res1Num)
	d Conversion	//$TS$	转换结果
	s result=code_ResultDeli_res_ResultDeli_res1_ItemDeli
	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"$$"_result,"Result")
	b ;a Result
    i $l(epis),$l(code) d ##Class(MI.Common.MIFBase).Save(mi, epis, result, date, time, QC)
    q
    
Conversion
	i $tr(res,"<")<20 s res="<20"
	q
	
ResultInfoTitle(rec)
	s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Data")=rec
	s codedata=^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Data")
	for j=1:1:$l(codedata,Deli) d
	.s codedataj=$p(codedata,Deli,j)
	.i codedataj=$g(^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Code","Epis")) d
	..s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Epis")=j
	.i codedataj=$g(^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Code","Code")) d
	..s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Code")=j
	.i codedataj=$g(^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Code","Res")) d
	..s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Res")=j
	.i codedataj=$g(^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Code","Res1")) d
	..s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Res1")=j
	q
	
ResultInfoTitleNew
	s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Data")=..#Data
	s codedata=^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Data")
	for j=1:1:$l(codedata,Deli) d
	.s codedataj=$p(codedata,Deli,j)
	.i codedataj=$g(^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Code","Epis")) d
	..s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Epis")=j
	.i codedataj=$g(^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Code","Code")) d
	..s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Code")=j
	.i codedataj=$g(^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Code","Res")) d
	..s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Res")=j
	.i codedataj=$g(^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Code","Res1")) d
	..s ^LISMachineEpis(mi,"Num","Res1")=j
	q
}

}

MIFEDAN(mi) 
	///仪器名称:	血气
	///仪器型号:	EDAN115
	///仪器厂商:	EDAN
	///通信协议:	HL7
	///交互方式:	单 向
	///接    口:	TCP/IP,RS232	
	///备    注:	 
    S mi=$G(mi) 
    Q:'$L(mi)
  
	s par11=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),12) 		//项目分隔符
	s par10=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),13) 	//结果分隔符
	s AntDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),14) 		//抗生素分隔符
	s SenDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),15) 		//药敏结果分隔符
	s par4="|TCP|"_$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),17)  	//端口号
    S stx=$C(2),etx=$C(3),ack=$C(6),enq=$C(5),eot=$C(4),etb=$C(23)
    S sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)  
    S lf=$C(10),nak=$C(21),(AllRecord,result,epis)="",kk=1
    S $ZT="ErrHandler",$EC=""
    S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,errFlag,resultType)=""
    Q:$$StartUTF8^MI.MIF000(mi)
	F {
		D Main
		Q:$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
	}
    C par4
    Q
    
Main R *R:10
	Q:'$TEST	//如果超时则退出
	Q:$c(R)'=sb   //以sb开头
	S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,errFlag,resultType,msgType,barcode,mshStr)=""
	S startTime=$P($H,",",2)
	K PLIST
	S index=1
	F {
		S curTime=$P($H,",",2)
		Q:curTime>(startTime+300)  //5分钟内没有处理完则退出循环
		Q:$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
		R *R:10
		Q:'$TEST	//如果超时则退出
		I $L($G(PLIST(index)))>=32700 {  //32767
			S index=+$O(PLIST(""),-1)+1
			S PLIST(index)=""
		}
		I $C(R)'=eb,$C(R)'=cr {
			S PLIST(index)=$G(PLIST(index))_$C(R)
		}
		I $C(R)=cr {  	//解析一条记录
			D Record
			K PLIST
			S index=1	
		}	
		Q:$C(R)=eb   	//循环读取,当为eb的时候则退出
	}
	D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,result,"result")
	D Save
	Q
	
Record
    S index=""
    S segmentType="",dataTye="",graphType="",base64Stream=""
    S isImage=0,isBinary=0
    F {
		S index=$O(PLIST(index))
		Q:'$L(index)
		S record=$TR($G(PLIST(index)),cr)
		Continue:'$L(record)
		D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"H<--M")
		I index=1 {
			S segmentType=$P(record,"|",1)
			I segmentType="MSH" {	//信息头信息
				S mshStr=record
				//消息类型
    			S msgType=$P($P(record,"|",9),"^",1)  //ORU,ACK,QRY,QCK,DSR	
    			I msgType="ORU" {
	    			D SendACK(mi,record,"AA",0,"Message accepted")
	    		}
	    		I msgType="ORM" {
	    		}
	    		S resultType=$P(record,"|",11)
			}
			
			I segmentType="PID" {	//患者信息
					
			}
			
			I segmentType="PVI" {	//就诊信息
					
			}
			
			I segmentType="OBR" {	//医嘱信息
				S epis=$P(record,"|",3) 
    			S:'$l(epis) epis=$P(record,"|",4)
	     		S code=$P($P(record,"|",5),"^",1)
	     		I code="00003" {	//LJ QCR
		     		
		     	}
			}
			
			
			I segmentType="OBX" {
				S dataTye=$P(record,"|",3)  //NM (numeric) 表示数字值，用于定量项目,
     										//ST (string) 表示字符串值，用于定性项目
    			S channel=$P(record,"|",5)
    			;S channel=$P(channel,"^",2)
    			S value=$P(record,"|",6)
    			
    			I channel="SI" {	//value=浊度(L)^溶血(H)^黄疸(I)
	    			S:$l($P(value,"^",2)) result=result_channel_"H"_$C(92)_$P(value,"^",2)_$C(44)
	    			S:$l($P(value,"^",3)) result=result_channel_"I"_$C(92)_$P(value,"^",3)_$C(44)
	    			S value=$P(value,"^",1)
	    		}
    			I dataTye="ST" {
    				;S value=$S(value="ò?D?":"阴性",value="??D?":"阳性",1:value)
    			}
    			I $L(channel),dataTye'="ED",dataTye'="IS" {
	    			S result=result_channel_$C(92)_value_$C(44)
    			}
    			S channel=$p($P(record,"|",4),"^",1)
    			I dataTye="IS" {	  
	    			I channel="05001",resultType="Q" {		//质控浓度
		    			S epis=value	
		    		}
	    		}
    			S graphTypeDesc=$ZCVT($P($P(record,"|",4),"^",2),"U")
    			S channel=$P($P(record,"|",4),"^",1)
    			I dataTye="ED" {	//图形数据
    				I $ZCVT($P(value,"^",2),"U")=$ZCVT("Image","U") {
	    				S isImage=1  	//位图数据
	    			}
	    			I $ZCVT($P(value,"^",3),"U")=$ZCVT("Octer-stream","U") {
		    			S isBinary=1	//二进制数据(需要绘图)
		    		}
    				S graphType=channel
    				I channel="15050" {	//二进制数据
	    				S graphType="RBC"
	    			}

	    			}
	    			I channel="15354" {	//二进制数据
	    				S (isImage,isBinary)=0	//暂时不处理二进制数据
	    				S graphType="NRBC"
	    			}
	    			S graphData=$P(value,"^",5)
	    			
	    			S graphDataType=$P(value,"^",4)
	    			I $ZCVT(graphDataType,"U")=$ZCVT("Base64","U") {
	    				S base64Stream=##Class(%GlobalCharacterStream).%New()
	    				D base64Stream.Write(graphData)
	    			}
	    		}
			}
			
			I segmentType="ORC" {	//就诊信息
				S barcode=$P(record,"|",4)
				//S:$ZCVT(barcode,"U")=$ZCVT("Invalid","U") barcode=""  //条码扫描错误
				//I $L(barcode) {  //双向	
				//} Invalid 条码扫描错误
				d SendORR(mi,record,"AA",0,"Message accepted",mshStr,barcode)
			}	
		}
		
		I dataTye="ED",index>1,$L(base64Stream) {
			D base64Stream.Write($P(record,"|",1))	
		}
	}
    
	I $L(base64Stream) {  //保存图形
		S graphOrder=0
		I isImage {   //位图格式
			S title=graphType
			S error=##Class(MI.Instrument).SaveBase64StreamToGraph(base64Stream,mi,epis,graphType,graphOrder,title,"")
			I $L(error) {
				D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$TR(error,"^","--"),"Graph Error")	
			}
		} ELSE {
			I isBinary {
				D SaveHistogram(mi,epis,graphType,graphOrder,base64Stream)
			}
		}
		K base64Stream
	}
    Q
  
 
Save  
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"^"_result,"Test")	
  	I $l(epis),$l(result) {
	  	S QC=""
  		D Save^MI.MIF000(mi,epis,result,date,time,QC)
  	}
  	S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,resultType)=""
  	Q
  
SendACK(mi,mshStr,ackType="AA",errCode=0,errDesc="Message accepted") //send 'ack' to instrument 
    N (mi,mshStr,ackType,errCode,errDesc)
    S mi=$g(mi),mshStr=$g(mshStr),ackType=$g(ackType),errCode=$g(errCode),errDesc=$g(errDesc)
    S ret=1,sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)
    Q:('$l(mi))||('$l(mshStr)) ret
    S mshStr=$TR(mshStr,cr,"")
    //Q:$l(mshStr,"|")<21 ret
    S ret=0
    S msgRoutine=$P($P(mshStr,"|",9),"^",2)
    S seq=$P(mshStr,"|",10)
    S mshStr=$P(mshStr,"|",1,2)_"|LIS|||"_$P(mshStr,"|",6,$l(mshStr))
    
    S $P(mshStr,"|",9)="ACK^"_msgRoutine
    W sb,mshStr,cr,"MSA|"_ackType_"|"_seq_"|"_errDesc_"|||"_errCode_"|",cr,eb,cr,*-3
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$S(ackType="AA":"ACK",ackType="AE":"Error",ackType="AR":"NAK",1:"NULL"),"H-->M")
    Q ret
    
ErrHandler
	D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$TR($ZERROR,"^","--")_".错误代码:"_$ECODE,"Runtime Error")
    Q 
    
    //保存直方图
SaveHistogram(mi,epis,graphType,graphOrder,base64Stream)
    N (mi,epis,graphType,graphOrder,base64Stream)
    S mi=$G(mi),epis=$G(epis),graphType=$G(graphType),graphOrder=$G(graphOrder),base64Stream=$G(base64Stream)
    Q:'$L(mi) 1
    Q:'$L(epis) 1
    Q:'$L(base64Stream) 1
    Q:'$L(graphType) 1
    S:'$L(graphOrder) graphOrder=0
    S glBinaryStream=##Class(%GlobalBinaryStream).%New()
    While 'base64Stream.AtEnd {
	    S base64=base64Stream.Read()
	    S binary=$system.Encryption.Base64Decode(base64)
	    D glBinaryStream.Write(binary)
	}
	
	S charStream=##Class(%GlobalCharacterStream).%New()
	S maxDot=0
	While 'glBinaryStream.AtEnd {
	    S char=glBinaryStream.Read(1)
	    S ascValue=$ASCII(char)_","
	    S maxDot=maxDot+1
	    D charStream.Write(ascValue)
	}
	D charStream.Write("0")
	K glBinaryStream
	S title=graphType
	S foreColor=12
	S:graphType="PLT" foreColor=10
	S top=10
	S left=10
	S width=300
	S height=150
	S (label,maxValue,memo)=""
    S error=##Class(MI.Instrument).SaveHistogram(charStream,mi,epis,graphType,graphOrder,label,title,maxDot,maxValue,memo,foreColor,top,left,width,height)
    I $L(error) {
		D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$TR(error,"^","--"),"Graph Error")	
	}
    K charStream
    Q 0
    
SendORR(mi,record, AckType="AA",ErrCode=0,ErrDesc="Message accepted",mshStr,epis)
	 N (mi,record,AckType,ErrCode,ErrDesc,mshStr,epis)
	 s mi=$g(mi),record=$g(record),AckType=$g(AckType),ErrCode=$g(ErrCode),ErrDesc=$g(ErrDesc),mshStr=$g(mshStr),epis=$g(epis)
	 S ret=1,sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)
	 Q:('$l(mi))||('$l(mshStr)) ret
	 S mshStr=$TR(mshStr,cr,"")	
	 S ret=0
	 S seq=$P(mshStr,"|",10)
	 S mshStr=$P(mshStr,"|",1,2)_"|LIS||||"_$P(mshStr,"|",7,$l(mshStr))
   	 S $P(mshStr,"|",9)="ORR^O02"
   	 s isRecieve=""
   	 s wgDR=""
   	 s wgDR=$lg(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),6)
	 //&sql(SELECT EpisodeNo into :isRecieve FROM dbo.RP_VisitNumberReport where AssayNo=:epis and WorkGroupMachineDR=:wgDR)
	 s isRecieve=epis //##class(HIS.DHCReportPrint).GetReportAssayNoMTHD(mi,epis)
	 s flag="AA"
	 s MSACode=seq
	 D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,isRecieve,"isRecieve is ")
	 i ($l(isRecieve)<1)
	 {
		 s flag="AR"
	 }
	 i $ZCVT(epis,"U")=$ZCVT("Invalid","U"){
		 s flag="AR"
	 }
	 s MSA="MSA|"_flag_"|"_MSACode
	 i flag="AR"{
		 S TMPCORDE=sb_mshStr_cr_MSA_cr_eb_cr
		 W sb,mshStr,cr,MSA,cr,eb,cr,*-3
		 D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,TMPCORDE,"H->M")
	 }else{
	 s PatInfomation=""
	 s PatInfomation=$$GetPatInfo(epis,mi)
	 D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,PatInfomation,"PatInfomation is")
	 s (RegNo,Name,Birth,Species,PatType,LOC,BedNo,Fee,Srcdocno,PatAge)=""
	 if $l(PatInfomation){
	 s RegNo=$p(PatInfomation,",",9)
	 s Name=$p(PatInfomation,",",10)
	 s Birth=$p(PatInfomation,",",29)
	 s Species=$p(PatInfomation,",",11)
	 i Species="1" s Species="Male"
	 i Species="2" s Species="Fmale"
	 s PatType=$p(PatInfomation,",",12)
	 s LOC=$p(PatInfomation,",",6)
	 s BedNo=$p(PatInfomation,",",13)
	 s Fee=$p(PatInfomation,",",5)
	 s Srcdocno=$p(PatInfomation,",",7)
	 s PatAge=$p(PatInfomation,",",14)
	 }
	 s PID="PID|1||"_RegNo_"^^^^MR||"_Name_"||"_Birth_"|"_Species
	 s PV1="PV1|1|"_PatType_"|"_LOC_"^^"_BedNo_"|||||||||||||||||"_Fee
	 s ORC="ORC|AF||"_epis
	 s curTime=$zd($h,8)_$tr($zt($p($h,",",2)),":","")
	 s randomNumber=1000+$r(1000)
	 s OBR="OBR|1|"_epis_"||00001^Automated Count^99MRC||"_curTime_randomNumber_"||||"_Srcdocno_"||||||||||||||HM||||||||Bill"
	 s TestCodeDate=""
	 s TestCodeDate=$$SearchTestItem(mi,epis)
	 s OBX="OBX|1|IS|08003^Test Mode^99MRC||"_TestCodeDate_"||||||F"_cr_
			"OBX|2|IS|01002^Ref Group^99MRC||Child||||||F"_cr_
			"OBX|3|NM|30525-0^Age^LN||"_PatAge_"|yr|||||F"_cr_
			"OBX|4|ST|01001^Remark^99MRC||"_PatType_"||||||F"_cr_
			"OBX|5|ST|08005^SerialNumber^99MRC||"_isRecieve_"||||||F"_cr_
			"OBX|6|IS|01007^Sample Type^99MRC||Venous blood||||||"_cr_
			"OBX|7|IS|01008^Patient Area^99MRC||A - 501||||||F"_cr_
			"OBX|8|ST|01009^Custom patient info 1^99MRC||Nothing||||||F"_cr_
			"OBX|9|ST|01010^Custom patient info 2^99MRC||Nothing||||||F"_cr_
			"OBX|10|ST|01011^Custom patient info 3^99MRC||Nothing||||||F"
		S TMPORDER=sb_mshStr_cr_MSA_cr_PID_cr_PV1_cr_ORC_cr_OBR_cr_OBX_cr_eb_cr
		w sb,mshStr,cr,MSA,cr,PID,cr,PV1,cr,ORC,cr,OBR,cr,OBX,cr,eb,cr,*-3
		D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,TMPORDER,"H->M")
	 }
	Q ret
SearchTestItem(mi,epis)
	S tcx="CBC",tc=""
	d ScanOne^MI.MIF000(mi,epis)
	s chl="" f  s chl=$o(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,epis,chl)) q:chl=""  d 
  	.i chl["NEUT" s tcx=tcx_"+DIFF" 
  	.i chl["RET" s tcx=tcx_"+RET" 
    .i chl["CRP" s tcx=tcx_"+CRP"
    //解决遍历通道索引顺序问题漏项
    i tcx["DIFF" s tc="CBC+DIFF"
    i tcx["RET" s tc="CBC+DIFF+RET"
    i tcx["CRP" s tc="CBC+DIFF+CRP"
    Q tc
GetPatInfo(labno,mi)
    s labno = $g(labno),mi=$g(mi)
	i $l(labno)=0 q ""
	s VisitNumberDR = $o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber"," "_labno,""))
	i '$l(VisitNumberDR) q ""
	//标本信息
	s RPVisitNumberData=$g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(VisitNumberDR))
	s LocationDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,22),Location=""
	i $l(LocationDR) s Location=$lg($g(^dbo.BTLocationD(LocationDR)),3)
	s DoctorDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,23),Doctor=""
	i $l(DoctorDR) s Doctor=$lg($g(^dbo.BTDoctorD(DoctorDR)),3)
	s ReceiveDate=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,66)
	s ReceiveTime=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,67)
	s ReceiveUserDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,68),ReceiveUser=""
	i $l(ReceiveUserDR) s ReceiveUser=$lg($g(^dbo.SYSUserD(ReceiveUserDR)),3)
	s RegNo=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,3)
	s SurName=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,13)
 	s GivenName=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,14)
	i SurName=GivenName s PatName=SurName
	e  s PatName=SurName_GivenName	
	s SpeciesDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,15),Species=""
	i $l(SpeciesDR) s Species=$lg($g(^dbo.BTSpeciesD(SpeciesDR)),3)
	s AdmTypeDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,4),AdmType=""
	i $l(AdmTypeDR) s AdmType=$lg($g(^dbo.BTAdmissionTypeD(AdmTypeDR)),2)
	s BedNo=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,27)
	s Age=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,18)
	s BirthDate=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,16)
	s AgeUnitDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,19),AgeUnit=""
	i $l(AgeUnitDR) s AgeUnit=$lg($g(^dbo.BTAgeUnitD(AgeUnitDR)),3)
	s CollectDate=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,51)
	s CollectTime=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,52)
	s Diagnose=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,28)
	
  	s Sampleda=$zd($p($h,",",1),3)_" "_$zt($p($h,",",2))
	s Instrument = "XN"
	i $l(mi) s Instrument=$lg(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),22)
	s Sampleno=labno   //检测号
	s Sampletype=""
 	s Feetype="" ;费别
	s Srcdepno=Location  ;送检科室
  	s Srcdocno=Doctor   ;送检医生
  	s Userno=ReceiveUser ;检验医生(录入者)
	s Patno=RegNo ;登记号 ""
	s BarCode=""
  	s Patna=PatName   ;病人姓名
	s Sex=1  ;性别
	i Species="男" s Sex="1"     ;1:男 ，2 女
	i Species ="女" s Sex="2"
  	s Pattype=AdmType   ;病人类型
  	s Bedno = BedNo    ;床号
  	s Patage=Age  ;年龄
  	s Ageunit=""   ;年龄单位
  	s Reqno=labno  ;申请号 = 检验号
	s Reqda=""
	i $l(ReceiveDate) s Reqda=$e(ReceiveDate,1,4)_"-"_$e(ReceiveDate,5,6)_"-"_$e(ReceiveDate,7,8)_" "_$zt(ReceiveTime,2) ;送检日期 = 接收时间
	s Reportda=""   ;报告日期  = 初审(保存结果)时间
	s Printflag=""  ;打印标志
	s Resultflag=""  ;结果标志
	s Errflag=""  ;错误标志
	s Diagnose = Diagnose   ;诊断
	s Description=""  ;备注
	s Reserve=""  ;保留字段
	s Patnamn=""   ;姓名拼音码
	i $l(CollectDate) s Getda=$e(CollectDate,1,4)_"-"_$e(CollectDate,5,6)_"-"_$e(CollectDate,7,8)_" "_$zt(CollectTime,2) 
	e  s Getda=Reqda ;接收时间/采样日期
	s Wardno=""  ;病区
	s RetString=""
	s EpisodeNo=""
	s Diagnose=""
	s RetString=Sampleda_","_Instrument_","_Sampleno_","_Sampletype_","_Feetype_","_Srcdepno_","_Srcdocno_","_Userno_","
	s RetString=RetString_Patno_","_Patna_","_Sex_","_Pattype_","_Bedno_","_Patage_","_Ageunit_","_Reqno_","_Reqda_","
	s RetString=RetString_Reportda_","_Printflag_","_Resultflag_","_Errflag_","_Diagnose_","_Description_","_Reserve_","
	s RetString=RetString_Patnamn_","_Getda_","_Wardno_","_BarCode_","_BirthDate_","_EpisodeNo
	q RetString

MIFKUF10(mi) 
	///仪器名称:	粪便分析仪
	///仪器型号:	KU-F10
	///仪器厂商:	珠海科域
	///通信协议:	HL7
	///交互方式:	单向
	///接    口:	TCP/IP,RS232	
	///编 写 者:	liuzf
	///编写日期:	2018-01-08
	///备    注:	仪器配置:选择HL7协议
	///接口版本:	V0.0.1
	///更新日志:
	///-1.更新日期:
	///---更 新 者:
	///---更新备注:    b
    S mi=$G(mi) 
    Q:'$L(mi)
  
	s par11=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),12) 		//项目分隔符
	s par10=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),13) 	//结果分隔符
	s AntDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),14) 		//抗生素分隔符
	s SenDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),15) 		//药敏结果分隔符
	s par4="|TCP|"_$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),17)  	//端口号

	S mi1=mi
    S stx=$C(2),etx=$C(3),ack=$C(6),enq=$C(5),eot=$C(4),etb=$C(23)
    S sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)  
    S lf=$C(10),nak=$C(21),(AllRecord,result,epis)="",kk=1
    //S $ZT="ErrHandler",$EC=""
    S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,errFlag,resultType)=""
    Q:$$StartUTF8^MI.MIF000(mi)
	F {
		D Main
		Q:$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
	}
    C par4
    Q
    
Main 
	S $ZT="ErrHandler",$EC="" 
	R *R:10
	Q:'$TEST	//如果超时则退出
	Q:$c(R)'=sb   //以sb开头
	S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,errFlag,resultType,msgType,barcode,mshStr)=""
	S startTime=$P($H,",",2)
	K PLIST
	S index=1
	F {
		S curTime=$P($H,",",2)
		Q:curTime>(startTime+300)  //5分钟内没有处理完则退出循环
		Q:$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
		R *R:10
		Q:'$TEST	//如果超时则退出
		I $L($G(PLIST(index)))>=32700 {  //32767
			S index=+$O(PLIST(""),-1)+1
			S PLIST(index)=""
		}
		I $C(R)'=eb,$C(R)'=cr {
			S PLIST(index)=$G(PLIST(index))_$C(R)
		}
		I ($C(R)=eb)||($c(R)=cr) {  	//解析一条记录
			D Record
			K PLIST
			S index=1	
		}	
		Q:$C(R)=eb   	//循环读取,当为eb的时候则退出
	}
	D Save
	Q
	
Record
    S index=""
    S segmentType="",dataTye="",graphType="",base64Stream=""
    S isImage=0,isBinary=0
    F {
		S index=$O(PLIST(index))
		Q:'$L(index)
		S record=$TR($G(PLIST(index)),cr)
		Continue:'$L(record)
		D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"H<--M")
		I index=1 {
			S segmentType=$P(record,"|",1)
			I segmentType="MSH" {	//信息头信息
				S mshStr=record
				//消息类型MSH|^~\&|RIS||||20221102092643||QRY^Q01|a94d57c6-34ac-4815-bf2d-273d71cacaac|P|2.4||||||UTF-8
    			S msgType=$P($P(record,"|",9),"^",1)  //ORU,ACK,QRY,QCK,DSR	
    			s MsgCode=$P(record,"|",10)
    			s ^TMPF800("MSH")=MsgCode
    			I msgType="ORU" {
	    			D SendACK(mi,record,"AA",0,"Message accepted")
	    		}
	    		I msgType="ORM" {
	    		}
	    		S resultType=$P(record,"|",11)
			}
			
			I segmentType="PID" {	//患者信息
				;S epis=$P(record,"|",4) 	
			}
			
			I segmentType="PVI" {	//就诊信息
					
			}
			
			I segmentType="OBR" {	//医嘱信息
				 S epis=$P(record,"|",3) 
    			i '$l(epis) s epis=$P(record,"|",4)
    			S dateStr=$P(record,"|",8)
     			I dateStr?14N {
	     			//S date=$ZDH($E(dateStr,1,4)_"-"_$E(dateStr,5,6)_"-"_$E(dateStr,7,8),3)
	     			//S time=$ZTH($E(dateStr,9,10)_":"_$E(dateStr,11,12)_":"_$E(dateStr,13,14),1)	
	     		}
	     		s positioninfo=$P(record,"|",11)
	     		try{D ##class(MI.Special.Common).SaveRackNo(epis,positioninfo,mi,"结果")}catch{}
	     		
			}
			
			I segmentType="OBX" {
				S dataTye=$P(record,"|",3)  //NM (numeric) 表示数字值，用于定量项目,
     										//ST (string) 表示字符串值，用于定性项目
    			S channel=$P(record,"|",4)
    			S channel=$P(channel,"^",2)
    			S value=$P(record,"|",6)
    			
    			i dataTye="ST"{
					i $l(channel),$l(value) s result=result_channel_par10_value_par11
    			}
    			i dataTye="WR"{
	    			s expertRules=$P(record,"|",6)
	    			try{d ##Class(MI.Special.Common).SaveAlarmInformation(mi,epis,expertRules)}catch{}
    			}
    			i dataTye="ED"{
					s imagetype=$tr(channel," ")
					s graphData=$p(value,"^",5)
					s filename=epis_imagetype_".bmp"
					try{s ret=$$SaveImage(mi,epis,imagetype,graphData,filename)}catch err{s ret=err.Data}
					D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,graphData,imagetype_":"_ret)
    			}
				
			}
			
			I segmentType="QRD" {	//双向查询
			// QRD|20221102092049|R|I|f04d46ad-f019-4870-a4e1-9d4c4cf0e86b|||9999^RD|900000054819|OTH|||T
				S barcode=$P(record,"|",9)
				s QRDCode=$P(record,"|",5)
				s ^TMPF800("QRD")=QRDCode
				
			}
			I segmentType="QRF" {	//就诊信息
			    I $L(barcode) {  //双向
					D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,barcode,"barcode")
					i $P(record,"|",6)'="0"{
						s positioninfo=$P(record,"|",5)_"^"_$P(record,"|",6)
						try{D ##class(MI.Special.Common).SaveRackNo(barcode,positioninfo,mi,"上机")}catch{}
					}
					d SendQRD(mi,record,barcode)
				}
			}	
		}
    }
    Q
  
 
Save  
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"^"_result,"Result")	
  	I $l(epis),$l(result) {
	  	S QC=""
  		D Save^MI.MIF000(mi,epis,result,date,time,QC)
  	}
  	S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,resultType)=""
  	Q
  
SendACK(mi,mshStr,ackType="AA",errCode=0,errDesc="Message accepted") //send 'ack' to instrument 
    N (mi,mshStr,ackType,errCode,errDesc)
    S mi=$g(mi),mshStr=$g(mshStr),ackType=$g(ackType),errCode=$g(errCode),errDesc=$g(errDesc)
    S ret=1,sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)
    Q:('$l(mi))||('$l(mshStr)) ret
    S mshStr=$TR(mshStr,cr,"")
    //Q:$l(mshStr,"|")<21 ret
    S ret=0
    S msgRoutine=$P($P(mshStr,"|",9),"^",2)
    S seq=$P(mshStr,"|",10)
    S mshStr=$P(mshStr,"|",1,2)_"|LIS|||"_$P(mshStr,"|",6,$l(mshStr))
    
    S $P(mshStr,"|",9)="ACK^"_msgRoutine
    W sb,mshStr,cr,"MSA|"_ackType_"|"_seq_"|"_errDesc_"|||"_errCode_"|",cr,eb,cr,*-3
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$S(ackType="AA":"ACK",ackType="AE":"Error",ackType="AR":"NAK",1:"NULL"),"H-->M")
    Q ret
    
ErrHandler
	D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$TR($ZERROR,"^","--")_".错误代码:"_$ECODE,"Runtime Error")
    Q 

SendQRD(mi,record,labno)
	N (mi,record,AckType,ErrCode,ErrDesc,mshStr,labno)
	s mi=$g(mi),record=$g(record),AckType=$g(AckType),ErrCode=$g(ErrCode),ErrDesc=$g(ErrDesc),mshStr=$g(mshStr),labno=$g(labno)
	S ret=1,sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)
	Q:('$l(mi))||('$l(record))
 
    
	d ScanOne^MI.MIF000(mi,labno) ;创建上传化验项目列表
	s MM1=^TMPF800("MSH")
    s MM2=^TMPF800("QRD")
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,MM1_"^"_MM2,"MM")	
	S date=$tr($zd(+$h,3),"-")
	S time=$tr($zt($p($h,",",2)),":")
	s MSH="MSH|^~\&|LIS|ZF|RIS||"_date_time_"||DSR^Q01|"_MM1_"|P|2.4|||P|5||UTF-8"_cr
	s MSA="MSA|AA|"_MM1_cr
	s QRD="QRD|"_date_time_"|R|I|"_MM2_"|||RD|"_labno_"|OTH|||T"_cr
	s QRF="QRF|RIS|||||RCT|COR|ALL"_cr
	s VisitNumberDR = $o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",""_labno,""))
	//标本信息
	q:'$l(VisitNumberDR)
	s RPVisitNumberData=$g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(VisitNumberDR))
	s RegNo=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,3)
	s BedNo=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,27)
	s SurName=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,13)
	s Age=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,18)
	s SpeciesDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,15),Species=""
	i $l(SpeciesDR) s Species=$lg($g(^dbo.BTSpeciesD(SpeciesDR)),3)
	s DoctorDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,23),Doctor=""
	i $l(DoctorDR) s Doctor=$lg($g(^dbo.BTDoctorD(DoctorDR)),3)
	s LocationDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,22),Location=""
	i $l(LocationDR) s Location=$lg($g(^dbo.BTLocationD(LocationDR)),3)
	
	s DSP="DSP|1||"_RegNo_cr_
			"DSP|2||"_Age_cr_
			"DSP|3||"_SurName_cr_
			"DSP|4|||||"_cr_
			"DSP|5||"_Species_cr_
			"DSP|6||O"_cr_
			"DSP|7||"_cr_
			"DSP|8||"_cr_
			"DSP|9||"_cr_
			"DSP|10||"_cr_
			"DSP|11||"_cr_
			"DSP|12||"_cr_
			"DSP|13||"_cr_
			"DSP|14||"_cr_
			"DSP|15||"_cr_
			"DSP|16||"_cr_
			"DSP|17||"_cr_
			"DSP|18||"_cr_
			"DSP|19||"_cr_
			"DSP|20||"_cr_
			"DSP|21||"_labno_cr_
			"DSP|22||"_labno_cr_
			"DSP|23||"_$tr($zdt($h,3),"-: ")_"|||"_cr_
			"DSP|24||N"_cr_
			"DSP|25||1"_cr_
			"DSP|26||serum"_cr_
			"DSP|27||"_cr_
			"DSP|28||"_cr
	s TCx=""
	S chl="" F  S chl=$o(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,labno,chl)) Q:chl=""  D
	.s TCx=TCx_"+"_chl
	s TCx=$e(TCx,2,$l(TCx))
	s DSP=DSP_"DSP|29||"_TCx_cr
	
	
	
	s mshStr=MSH_MSA_QRD_QRF_DSP
	w sb,mshStr,eb,cr,*-3

/// 仪器主键，流水号，图片代码，base64串，图片名称	
SaveImage(mi,epis,imagetype,graphData,filename)
	S base64Stream=##Class(%GlobalCharacterStream).%New()
	D base64Stream.Write(graphData)
	S ftpFfolderName="F810"
	s ret=$$SaveGZIPBase64ToMachine(mi,epis,imagetype,base64Stream,filename,ftpFfolderName)
	q ret


/// 保存图片Base64串到仪器
/// mi:仪器主键(*必填)
/// epis:流水号(*必填)
/// ImageClass:图片类别(*必填)
/// base64Stream:图片的Base64流(*必填)
/// fileName:文件名
/// ftpFfolderName:文件服务的文件夹名称
/// w ##Class(MI.Common.DealImage).SaveGZIPBase64ToMachine("1","1","DIFF","","","")
SaveGZIPBase64ToMachine(mi,epis,ImageClass,base64Stream,fileName,ftpFfolderName)
	//传入字符串的自动转换流
	i '$IsObject(base64Stream) d
	.s base64StreamTmp=##class(%GlobalCharacterStream).%New()
	.d base64StreamTmp.Write(base64Stream)
	.s base64Stream=base64StreamTmp
	s retpath=$$DealGZipBase64Str(base64Stream,fileName,ftpFfolderName)
	i retpath["-1^" d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"路径:"_retpath_"不正常","H<--M")
	i retpath["-1^" q "-1^可能的非法路径"
	i $l(retpath)>300 q "-1^可能的非法路径"
	i retpath=$c(0) q "-1^绘图报错，请查看网站Logs里异常日志"
	s ret=1

/// D ##class(MI.Special.Common).SaveRackNo(labno, positioninfo, mi, typename, curWorkGroupMachineDR)
/// D ##class(MI.Special.Common).SaveRackNo("9000000193","50-1","6","上机")
ClassMethod SaveRackNo(labno, positioninfo, mi, typename, curWorkGroupMachineDR)
{
	s labno=$g(labno)
	s positioninfo=$g(positioninfo)
	s mi=$g(mi),curWorkGroupMachineDR=$g(curWorkGroupMachineDR),typename=$g(typename)
	i '$L(curWorkGroupMachineDR) s curWorkGroupMachineDR=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6)
	i $l(typename) s positioninfo=typename_":"_positioninfo
	s hasFindRep=0
	i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno))) d
	.s VisitNumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno),""))
	.i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR)) d
	..s WorkGroupMachineDR="" f  s WorkGroupMachineDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR,WorkGroupMachineDR)) q:WorkGroupMachineDR=""  d
	...s OrderNo="" f  s OrderNo=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR,WorkGroupMachineDR,OrderNo)) q:OrderNo=""  d
	....s ReportDR="" f  s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR,WorkGroupMachineDR,OrderNo,ReportDR)) q:ReportDR=""  d
	.....s WorkGroupMachineDR=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(ReportDR)),4) 
	.....s objrep=##Class(dbo.RPVisitNumberReport).%OpenId(ReportDR)
	.....i $l(objrep.RackNo),objrep.RackNo'=positioninfo try{j ..SaveRecord(labno,"架子号位置更新:"_objrep.RackNo_"-->"_positioninfo,mi,"101")}catch{}	//架子号更新
	.....s objrep.RackNo=positioninfo
	.....s sc=objrep.%Save()
	.....i typename="上机" try{j ..SaveRecord(labno,"仪器上机:"_positioninfo,mi,"6")}catch{}
	.....s hasFindRep=1
	.....i ('$SYSTEM.Status.IsOK(sc)) d
	......d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"-1^存"_typename_"信息失败:"_$SYSTEM.Status.GetErrorText(sc),"H<--M")
	i hasFindRep=0,$d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexEpisodeNo",$zd($h,8),curWorkGroupMachineDR,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno))) d
	.s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexEpisodeNo",$zd($h,8),curWorkGroupMachineDR,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno),""))
	.s objrep=##Class(dbo.RPVisitNumberReport).%OpenId(ReportDR)
	.i $l(objrep.RackNo),objrep.RackNo'=positioninfo try{j ..SaveRecord(labno,"架子号位置更新:"_objrep.RackNo_"-->"_positioninfo,mi,"101")}catch{}	//架子号更新
	.s objrep.RackNo=positioninfo
	.s sc=objrep.%Save()
	.i typename="上机" try{j ..SaveRecord(labno,"仪器上机:"_positioninfo,mi,"6")}catch{}
	.s hasFindRep=1
	i hasFindRep=0 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,labno_":没有找到报告","H<--M")
	q hasFindRep
}

/// Creator：      yanghaoran
/// CreatDate：    20240828
/// Description：  保存报警提示信息
/// Input：        mi 仪器主键,epis 流水号,expertRules 报警信息,expertRulesType 报警信息仪器类型(存在值将报警信息进行转换，不存在则直接保存报警信息)
/// 			   SaveTypeData (分隔符^)保存类型(1:次评价不打印，2:主评价可打印)，为空默认为1
/// 				   			是否保存未转换数据(1:保存，0:不保存)，为空默认为0
/// Output：   
/// DeBug:		   w ##Class(MI.Special.Common).SaveAlarmInformation(57,1200150259127,"CSCSCS") 
/// DeBug:		   w ##Class(MI.Special.Common).SaveAlarmInformation(2,1892,"Basophilia：嗜碱性粒细胞增加；NRBC?：有核红细胞？；Anisocytosis：红细胞大小不均；Macrocytosis：大红细胞症；Hypochromia：低色素性；WBC_Abn_Scattergram：白细胞异常散点图；IG_Present：幼稚粒细胞存在；PLT_Abn_Distribution：血小板异常直方图；Blasts/Abn_Lympho?：原始细胞/异常淋巴细胞?") 
/// DeBug:		   w ##Class(MI.Special.Common).SaveAlarmInformation(9,63,"13003","DMD7") 
ClassMethod SaveAlarmInformation(mi, epis, expertRules, expertRulesType, SaveTypeData)
{
	s mi=$g(mi)
    s epis=$g(epis)
    s expertRules=$g(expertRules)
    s SaveTypeData=$g(SaveTypeData)
    s SaveType=$p(SaveTypeData,"^",1)
    i '$l(SaveType) s SaveType=1		// 保存类型(1:次评价不打印，2:主评价可打印)，为空默认为1
    s expertRulesIsSave=$p(SaveTypeData,"^",2)
    i '$l(expertRulesIsSave) s expertRulesIsSave="0"	// 是否保存未转换数据(1:保存，0:不保存)，为空默认为0
    s expertRulesType=$g(expertRulesType)
  
    // 配置信息
    s Sep="；"	// 文本串分隔符
  
    // 转换报警信息
    i $l(expertRulesType) d
    .s InputInfo=""
    .s PoliceInfo=expertRules
    .i $l(PoliceInfo),$d(^LISPolice(expertRulesType,PoliceInfo)) d
  	..s InputInfo=$g(^LISPolice(expertRulesType,PoliceInfo))
  	..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,PoliceInfo_"$$"_InputInfo,"报警信息")
  	.i $l(InputInfo) d
  	..s expertRules=InputInfo
  	.e  d
  	..i expertRulesIsSave=0 d
  	...s expertRules=""
  	...d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"转换报警信息失败。","报警信息异常")
  	..e  d
  	...d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"保存原始报警信息。","报警信息异常")
  	i '$l(expertRules) q ""
  
    s ReportDR=$$GetReportID(mi,epis)
    i '$l(ReportDR) q ""
    s obj=##Class(dbo.RPVisitNumberReport).%OpenId(ReportDR)
    s TMPstr=obj.MinorConclusion
    i TMPstr'[expertRules d
    .i $l(TMPstr) d
    ..s Str=TMPstr_Sep_expertRules
    .e  d
    ..s Str=expertRules
    .s Str=$$DislodgeRepetition(Str,Sep)
    .i SaveType=1 d
    ..s obj.MinorConclusion=Str		//YHR 20230411 保存在报告次评价 不可打印
    .i SaveType=2 d
    ..s obj.MinorConclusion=Str		//YHR 20230411 保存在报告主评价 可打印
    s ret=obj.%Save()
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,ret_"$$"_expertRules,"SaveAlarmInformation")
    q ret
  
GetReportID(mi,AssayNo)
	// 根据仪器试验号获取报告ID
	s mi=$g(mi),AssayNo=$g(AssayNo)
	s ReportDR=""
	i '$l(AssayNo) q ReportDR
	s WGMachineID=$lg(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),6)
	i $D(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexMicNo",WGMachineID,AssayNo)) d
	.s TransmitDate=$zd($p($h,",",1),8)
	.s ReportDR=$O(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexMicNo",WGMachineID,AssayNo,TransmitDate,""),-1)
	i $l(ReportDR) q ReportDR
	i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",AssayNo)) d
	.s VisitnumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",AssayNo,""))
	.i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitnumberDR,WGMachineID,1)) d
	..s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitnumberDR,WGMachineID,1,""),-1)
	q ReportDR

DislodgeRepetition(Str,Sep)
	// 去除重复信息
	s Sep=$g(Sep)
	i '$l(Sep) s Sep="；"
	k ^LISTMPStr
	s ret=""
	f p=1:1:$l(Str,Sep) d
	.s Strp=$p(Str,Sep,p)
	.i '$l(Strp) q
	.s ^LISTMPStr("Data",Strp)=""
	s GStr="" f  s GStr=$o(^LISTMPStr("Data",GStr)) q:GStr=""  d
	.s ret=ret_Sep_GStr
	s ret=$e(ret,2,*)
	k ^LISTMPStr
	q ret
}

/// 保存图片Base64串到仪器
/// mi:仪器主键(*必填)
/// epis:流水号(*必填)
/// ImageClass:图片类别(*必填)
/// base64Stream:图片的Base64流(*必填)
/// fileName:文件名
/// ftpFfolderName:文件服务的文件夹名称
/// w ##Class(MI.Common.DealImage).SaveGZIPBase64ToMachine("1","1","DIFF","","","")
ClassMethod SaveGZIPBase64ToMachine(mi As %String, epis As %String, ImageClass As %String, base64Stream As %GlobalCharacterStream, fileName As %String, ftpFfolderName As %String) As %String
{
	//传入字符串的自动转换流
	i '$IsObject(base64Stream) d
	.s base64StreamTmp=##class(%GlobalCharacterStream).%New()
	.d base64StreamTmp.Write(base64Stream)
	.s base64Stream=base64StreamTmp
	s retpath=..DealGZipBase64Str(base64Stream,fileName,ftpFfolderName)
	i retpath["-1^" d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"路径:"_retpath_"不正常","H<--M")
	i retpath["-1^" q "-1^可能的非法路径"
	i $l(retpath)>300 q "-1^可能的非法路径"
	i retpath=$c(0) q "-1^绘图报错，请查看网站Logs里异常日志"
	s ret=1
  	i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q "-1^仪器不存在"
 	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_":"_ImageClass_":"_fileName,"H<--M")
 	s (ReceiveDate, ImageOrder, Caption, DisplayRatio, Height, Width, Sequence)=""
	s ret=##Class(MI.Common.MachineResult).SaveImage(ReceiveDate, epis, ImageClass, ImageOrder, retpath, mi, Caption, DisplayRatio, Height, Width, Sequence)
	i ret=0 s ret=1
	q ret
}

ClassMethod DealGZipBase64Str(base64Stream As %GlobalCharacterStream, fileName As %String, ftpFfolderName As %String, P3, P4, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %String

//// MI.MIFMKi1000
/// 名称: MI.MIFMKi1000
/// 描述: 迈克1000 仪器接口  
/// 通讯方式：双向
/// 编写者:BLiu
/// 编写日期: 20201125
MIFMKi1000(mi) ; 3/17/04 ; ASTM protocol - H7600
	s mi=$g(mi) 
	S ^TMPMACH10(mi,104)=$H
	i '$l(mi) q
	s ItemDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),12) //项目分隔符
	s ResultDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),13) //结果分隔符
	s AntDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),14) //抗生素分隔符
	s SenDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),15) //药敏结果分隔符
	s Port="|TCP|"_$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),17)  //端口号
	//控制字符
	SET $ZTRAP="ErrHandler"
	S iERR=0
	s stx=$c(2),etx=$c(3),ack=$c(6),enq=$c(5),eot=$c(4)
	s lf=$c(10),cr=$c(13),nak=$c(21),(result,epis)="",etb=$c(23)
	S ^TMPMACH10(mi,102)=$H
	i $$Start^MI.MIF000(mi) q
	f  d Main i $$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi) q
  	c Port
  	q
ErrHandler
	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$TR($ZERROR,"^","--")_".错误代码:"_$ECODE,"Runtime Error")
	s iERR=+$g(iERR)+1
	i iERR>30 s ret=$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
	h 10
    Q
Main r *R:10 e  d  q
  .d BUILD
  .//自动上传
  .d BUILD2
  i $c(R)=enq d
  .s AllRecord=""
  .d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"ENQ","H<--M")
  .d ACK
  .f  r *R:10 q:$c(R)=eot  d
  ..i $c(R)'=stx q
  ..s record=$$Read^MI.MIF000(mi,"",lf) q:'$l(record)

CHSUM(x) ; calculate check sum
  n (x) s z=0 f y=1:1:$l(x) s z=z+$a(x,y)
  s z=$e("0123456789ABCDEF",z#256\16+1)_$e("0123456789ABCDEF",z#16+1)
  q z
ACK  ; send 'ack' to instrument
  w ack,*-3
  d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"ACK","H-->M")

/// 名称: MI.MIFI3000
/// 描述: 深圳亚辉龙iFlash3000 仪器接口
/// 编写者:ZLS  
/// 编写日期: 20160925
/// 

MIFI3000(mi)   
    S mi=$G(mi) 
    Q:'$L(mi)
    s par11=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),12)      //项目分隔符
    s par10=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),13)  //结果分隔符
    s AntDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),14)        //抗生素分隔符
    s SenDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),15)        //药敏结果分隔符
    s par4="|TCP|"_$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),17)   //端口号
    S mi1=mi
    S stx=$C(2),etx=$C(3),ack=$C(6),enq=$C(5),eot=$C(4),etb=$C(23)
    S sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)  
    S lf=$C(10),nak=$C(21),(AllRecord,result,epis)="",kk=1
    S $ZT="ErrHandler",$EC=""
    S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,errFlag,resultType)=""
    Q:$$Start^MI.MIF000(mi)
    F {
        D Main
        Q:$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
    }
    C par4
    Q
    
Main R *R:10
    Q:'$TEST    //如果超时则退出
    Q:$c(R)'=sb   //以sb开头
    S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,errFlag,resultType,msgType,barcode,mshStr)=""
    S startTime=$P($H,",",2)
    K PLIST
    S index=1
    F {
        S curTime=$P($H,",",2)
        Q:curTime>(startTime+300)  //5分钟内没有处理完则退出循环
        Q:$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
        R *R:10
        Q:'$TEST    //如果超时则退出
        I $L($G(PLIST(index)))>=32700 {  //32767
            S index=+$O(PLIST(""),-1)+1
            S PLIST(index)=""
        }
        I $C(R)'=eb,$C(R)'=cr {
            S PLIST(index)=$G(PLIST(index))_$C(R)
        }
        I $C(R)=cr {    //解析一条记录
            D Record
            K PLIST
            S index=1   
        }   
        Q:$C(R)=eb      //循环读取,当为eb的时候则退出
    }
    D Save
    Q
    
Record
	K ^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi)
    S index=""
    S segmentType="",dataTye="",graphType=""
    S isImage=0,isBinary=0
    F {
        S index=$O(PLIST(index))
        Q:'$L(index)
        S record=$TR($G(PLIST(index)),cr)
        Continue:'$L(record)
        D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"H<--M")
        I index=1 {
            S segmentType=$P(record,"|",1)
          ;消息段(数据类型) 	MSH	  MSA 	PID   OBR  	OBX  ORD  QRF 	ERR   QAK    DSP     DSC     
            I segmentType="MSH" {   //信息头信息
                S mshStr=record
                //消息类型
                S msgType=$P($P(record,"|",9),"^",1)  //ORU,ACK,QRY,QCK,DSR 
                I msgType="ORU" {
                    D SendACK(mi,record,"AA",0,"Message accepted")
                }
                I msgType="ORM" {
                }
                I msgType="QRY" {
	                D SendQryACK(mi,record,"AA",0,"Message accepted")
                }
                S resultType=$P(record,"|",11)
            }
            
            I segmentType="PID" {   //患者信息
                    
            }
            
            I segmentType="PVI" {   //就诊信息
                    
            }
            
            I segmentType="OBR" {   //医嘱信息
                S epis=$P(record,"|",3) 
                S:'$l(epis) epis=$P(record,"|",4)
                S dateStr=$P(record,"|",8)
                I dateStr?14N {
                    S date=$ZDH($E(dateStr,1,4)_"-"_$E(dateStr,5,6)_"-"_$E(dateStr,7,8),3)
                    S time=$ZTH($E(dateStr,9,10)_":"_$E(dateStr,11,12)_":"_$E(dateStr,13,14),1) 
                }
                S code=$P($P(record,"|",5),"^",1)
            }
            
            I segmentType="OBX" {
                S dataTye=$P(record,"|",3)  //NM (numeric) 表示数字值，用于定量项目,
                                            //ST (string) 表示字符串值，用于定性项目
                S channel=$P(record,"|",4)
                S channel=$P(channel,"^",1)
                S value=$P(record,"|",6)
                
                I $L(channel),dataTye'="ED",dataTye'="IS" {
                    S result=result_channel_par10_value_par11
                }
            }
            
 			//根据条码号获取LIS标本
            I segmentType="QRD" {
                S barcode=$P(record,"|",9)  //QRD|20161208150935|R|D|1|||RD|16120703726|OTH|||T|
                I $L(barcode) {
	                S ^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",barcode,"MSH")=mshStr
	                S ^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",barcode,"QRD")=record
                }
            }
            //根据查询条件获取LIS标本
            I segmentType="QRF" { 
            	S tRecord=record	
            	S record=$TR(record," ")
            	S qryStartDate=$P(record,"|",3)
                S qryEndDate=$P(record,"|",4)
                S sampleIdStart=$P(record,"|",5)
                S sampleIdEnd=$P(record,"|",6)
                S:'$L(qryStartDate) qryStartDate=qryEndDate
                S:'$L(qryEndDate) qryEndDate=qryStartDate
                S:'$L(sampleIdStart) sampleIdStart=sampleIdEnd
                S:'$L(sampleIdEnd) sampleIdEnd=sampleIdStart
                //通过样本号段查询  QRF|iFlash3000|||1|9|RCT|COR|ALL|| 
                I sampleIdStart?1.N,sampleIdEnd?1.N {
	                F sampleId=sampleIdStart:1:sampleIdEnd {
		                S ^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"S",sampleId,"MSH")=mshStr
		                S ^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"S",sampleId,"QRF")=tRecord
		            }
	            }
	            //通过时间段查询	QRF|iFlash3000|20160122080000|20160122120000|||RCT|COR|ALL||
	            I qryStartDate?1.N,qryEndDate?1.N {
	                F qryDate=qryStartDate:1:qryEndDate {
		                S ^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"D",qryDate,"MSH")=mshStr
		                S ^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"D",qryDate,"QRF")=tRecord
		            }
	            }
            }
        }
    }
    
    //根本样本号获取条码号
    S sampleId=""
    F {
		S sampleId=$O(^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",sampleId))
	    Q:'$L(sampleId) 
	    //暂不处理
	}
	
	//根本日期获取条码号
    S qryDate=""
    F {
		S qryDate=$O(^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"D",qryDate))
	    Q:'$L(qryDate) 
	    //暂不处理
	}
	
	//上传标本
    S barcode="",barcodeIndex=0
    F {
	    S barcode=$O(^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",barcode))
	    Q:'$L(barcode)
	    S mshStr=$G(^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",barcode))
	    S barcodeIndex=barcodeIndex+1
	    I $O(^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",barcode))="" {
		    S barcodeIndex=""  //最后一个为空
		}
		S mshStr=$G(^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",barcode,"MSH"))
		S qrdStr=$G(^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",barcode,"QRD"))
		S qrfStr=$G(^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",barcode,"QRF"))
		I '$L(qrdStr) {
			S qrdStr="QRD|"_$TR($ZDT($H,8)," :")_"|R|D|1|||RD||OTH|||T|"	
		}
		I '$L(qrfStr) {
			S qrfStr="QRF|iFlash3000|||||RCT|COR|ALL||"	
		}
		S $P(qrdStr,"|",9)=""
	    S ret=$$SendOrder(mi,mshStr,qrdStr,qrfStr,barcode,barcodeIndex)
	}
	
	K ^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi)
    Q
  
 
Save  
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"^"_result,"Test")    
    I $l(epis),$l(result) {
        S QC=""
        S result=$$TransResult(mi,result)
        D Save^MI.MIF000(mi,epis,result,date,time,QC)
    }
    S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,resultType)=""
    Q
  
SendACK(mi,mshStr,ackType="AA",errCode=0,errDesc="Message accepted") //send 'ack' to instrument 
    N (mi,mshStr,ackType,errCode,errDesc)
    S mi=$g(mi),mshStr=$g(mshStr),ackType=$g(ackType),errCode=$g(errCode),errDesc=$g(errDesc)
    S ret=1,sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)
    Q:('$l(mi))||('$l(mshStr)) ret
    S mshStr=$TR(mshStr,cr,"")
    //Q:$l(mshStr,"|")<21 ret
    S ret=0
    S msgRoutine=$P($P(mshStr,"|",9),"^",2)
    S seq=$P(mshStr,"|",10)
    S mshStr=$P(mshStr,"|",1,2)_"|LIS|||"_$P(mshStr,"|",6,$l(mshStr))
    S $P(mshStr,"|",9)="ACK^"_msgRoutine
    W sb,mshStr,cr,"MSA|"_ackType_"|"_seq_"|"_errDesc_"|||"_errCode_"|",cr,eb,cr,*-3
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$S(ackType="AA":"ACK",ackType="AE":"Error",ackType="AR":"NAK",1:"NULL"),"H-->M")
    Q ret
    
SendQryACK(mi,mshStr,ackType="AA",errCode=0,errDesc="Message accepted") //send 'ack' to instrument 
    N (mi,mshStr,ackType,errCode,errDesc)
    S mi=$g(mi),mshStr=$g(mshStr),ackType=$g(ackType),errCode=$g(errCode),errDesc=$g(errDesc)
    S ret=1,sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)
    Q:('$l(mi))||('$l(mshStr)) ret
    S mshStr=$TR(mshStr,cr,"")
    S ret=0
    S msgRoutine=$P($P(mshStr,"|",9),"^",2)
    S seq=$P(mshStr,"|",10)
    S mshStr=$P(mshStr,"|",1,2)_"|LIS|||"_$P(mshStr,"|",6,$l(mshStr))
    S $P(mshStr,"|",9)="QCK^"_msgRoutine
    W sb,mshStr,cr,"MSA|"_ackType_"|"_seq_"|"_errDesc_"|||"_errCode_"|",cr,"ERR|0|",cr,"QAK|SR|OK|",cr,eb,cr,*-3
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$S(ackType="AA":"QACK",ackType="AE":"Error",ackType="AR":"QNAK",1:"NULL"),"H-->M")
    Q ret
    
ErrHandler
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$TR($ZERROR,"^","--")_".错误代码:"_$ECODE,"Runtime Error")
    Q 
    
    //双向上传医嘱信息,wwh,2015-11-05
SendOrder(mi,mshStr,qrdStr,qrfStr,barcode,DSC)
    N (mi,mshStr,qrdStr,qrfStr,barcode,DSC)
    S mi=$G(mi),mshStr=$G(mshStr),barcode=$G(barcode),DSC=$G(DSC),qrdStr=$G(qrdStr),qrfStr=$G(qrfStr)
    S sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)
    I '$L(barcode) {
        D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"条码号为空","Upload Error")   
        Q 1 
    }
    I $ZCVT(barcode,"U")=$ZCVT("Invalid","U") {             //条码扫描错误
        D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"条码扫描错误,机器未识别","Upload Error")    
        Q 1
    } 
    S labno=barcode
    S workGroupMachineDR=$LG($G(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6)
    S visiNumberDR=$O(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber"," "_labno,""))
    I '$L(visiNumberDR) {
        D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"在检验系统未找到条码:"_labno_"对应的标本信息,确定条码正确或标本已经接收?","Upload Error")    
        Q 1
    }
    S visNumberObj=##Class(dbo.RPVisitNumber).%OpenId(visiNumberDR)
    I '$L(visNumberObj) {
        D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"在检验系统未找到条码:"_labno_"对应的标本信息,确定条码正确或标本已经接收?","Upload Error")    
        Q 1
    }
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,labno,"Upload Start")
    K ^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,labno)
	D ScanOne^MI.MIF000(mi,labno)
    S result=""
	S chlStr=""
	S chl="",chlCnt=29
	F {
		S chl=$O(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,labno,chl))
		Q:'$L(chl)
		S chlStr=chlStr_"DSP|"_chlCnt_"||"_chl_"^^^|||"_cr
		S chlCnt=chlCnt+1
		S result=result_chl_$C(92)_"?"_$C(44)
	}
 	I '$L(chlStr) {
	 	D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"在检验系统未找到条码:"_labno_"对应的化验项目信息,确定医嘱或项目维护正确?","Upload Error")    
        Q 1
	}
	D Save^MI.MIF000(mi,labno,result,"","","")
	
	S specimenDR=$LG($G(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(visiNumberDR)),56)
	S specimenName=""
	S:$L(specimenDR) specimenName=$LG($G(^dbo.BTSpecimenD(specimenDR)),3)
	S sampleType="其他"
	I $L(specimenName),",血清,血浆,尿液,脑脊液,"[(","_specimenName_",") {
		S sampleType=specimenName
	}
	S birdthday=visNumberObj.BirthDate
	S:$L(birdthday)=8 birdthday=birdthday_"000000"
	S:'$L(mshStr) mshStr="MSH|^~\&|YHLO|iFlash3000|||20161208150935||QRY^Q02|18|P|2.3.1||||||ASCII|||"
    S mshSeq=$P(mshStr,"|",10)
    S $P(mshStr,"|",9)="DSR^Q03"
    S mshStr=$P(mshStr,"|",1,2)_"|LIS|||"_$P(mshStr,"|",6,$l(mshStr))
    
    S episode=""
    S workGroupMachineDR=##Class(MI.Instrument).GetWorkGroupMachineRowId(mi)
    I $L(workGroupMachineDR) {
    	S OrderNo=$O(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",visiNumberDR,workGroupMachineDR,""))
    	I $L(OrderNo) {
	    	S reportDR=$O(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",visiNumberDR,workGroupMachineDR,OrderNo,""))
	    	S episode=##Class(LIS.Core.Report).GetEpisodeNumber(reportDR)
	    }
    }
    
	S order=mshStr_cr //"MSH|^~\&|||||20160122110540||DSR^Q03|14|P|2.3.1||||||ASCII|||"_cr
	S order=order_"MSA|AA|"_mshSeq_"|Message accepted|||0|"_cr
	S order=order_"ERR|0|"_cr
	S order=order_"QAK|SR|OK|"_cr
	S order=order_qrdStr_cr  //"QRD|20160122110540|R|D|1|||RD||OTH|||T|"_cr
	S order=order_qrfStr_cr  //"QRF|iFlash3000|||||RCT|COR|ALL||"_cr
	S order=order_"DSP|1||"_visNumberObj.RegNo_"|||"_cr		//住院号
	S order=order_"DSP|2||"_episode_"|||"_cr		//床号
	//S order=order_"DSP|3||"_visNumberObj.SurName_"|||"_cr	//病人姓名
	S order=order_"DSP|3||"_episode_"|||"_cr	//病人姓名
	S order=order_"DSP|4||"_birdthday_"|||"_cr				//出生日期
	S order=order_"DSP|5||"_$S(visNumberObj.SpeciesDR=1:"M",visNumberObj.SpeciesDR=2:"F",1:"O")_"|||"_cr	//性别
	S order=order_"DSP|6|||||"_cr				//血型
	S order=order_"DSP|7|||||"_cr				//种族
	S order=order_"DSP|8|||||"_cr				//地址
	S order=order_"DSP|9|||||"_cr				//邮编
	S order=order_"DSP|10|||||"_cr				//家庭电话
	S order=order_"DSP|11|||||"_cr				//样本位
	S order=order_"DSP|12|||||"_cr				//样本采集时间
	S order=order_"DSP|13|||||"_cr				//未用
	S order=order_"DSP|14|||||"_cr				//未用
	S order=order_"DSP|15|||||"_cr				//病人类别
	S order=order_"DSP|16|||||"_cr				//医保帐号
	S order=order_"DSP|17|||||"_cr				//收费类型
	S order=order_"DSP|18|||||"_cr				//民族
	S order=order_"DSP|19|||||"_cr				//籍贯
	S order=order_"DSP|20|||||"_cr				//国家
	S order=order_"DSP|21||"_barcode_"|||"_cr	//*样本条码
	S order=order_"DSP|22||"_barcode_"|||"_cr	//*样本编号
	S order=order_"DSP|23|||||"_cr				//送检时间
	S order=order_"DSP|24||"_$S(visNumberObj.Urgent=1:"Y",1:"N")_"|||"_cr				//*是否急诊
	S order=order_"DSP|25|||||"_cr				//未用
	S order=order_"DSP|26||"_sampleType_"|||"_cr	//*样本类型(血清,血浆,尿液,脑脊液,其他)
	S order=order_"DSP|27|||||"_cr	//送检医生
	S order=order_"DSP|28|||||"_cr		//送检科室
	S order=order_chlStr
	S order=order_"DSC|"_DSC_"|"_cr
    W sb,order,eb,cr,*-3
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,sb_order_eb_cr,"H-->M") 
    //$TR($ZDT($H,8)," :") 
    Q 0
    
    //d Test^MI.MIFI3000("31",16112803586)
Test(mi,barcode)
    N (mi,barcode)
    S mi=$G(mi),barcode=$G(barcode)
    S mshStr="MSH|^~\&|YHLO|iFlash3000|||20160122110540||QRY^Q02|14|P|2.3.1||||||ASCII|||"
    S DSC=""
    S qrdStr="QRD|20160122110540|R|D|1|||RD|BarCode1|OTH|||T|"
    S qrfStr="QRF|iFlash3000|||||RCT|COR|ALL||"
    
    S sb="<SB>",eb="<EB>",cr="<CR>"
    I '$L(barcode) {
        W "条码号为空",!
        Q 1 
    }
    I $ZCVT(barcode,"U")=$ZCVT("Invalid","U") {             //条码扫描错误
        W "条码扫描错误,机器未识别",!   
        Q 1
    } 
    S labno=barcode
    S workGroupMachineDR=$LG($G(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6)
    S visiNumberDR=$O(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber"," "_labno,""))
    I '$L(visiNumberDR) {
    	W "条码未接收",!   
        Q 1 
    }
    I '$L(visiNumberDR) {
        W "在检验系统未找到条码:"_labno_"对应的标本信息,确定条码正确或标本已经接收?",!  
        Q 1
    }
    S visNumberObj=##Class(dbo.RPVisitNumber).%OpenId(visiNumberDR)
    I '$L(visNumberObj) {
        W "在检验系统未找到条码:"_labno_"对应的标本信息,确定条码正确或标本已经接收?",!   
        Q 1
    }
    K ^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,labno)
	D ScanOne^MI.MIF000(mi,labno)
	S chlStr=""
	S chl="",chlCnt=29
	F {
		S chl=$O(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,labno,chl))
		Q:'$L(chl)
		S chlStr=chlStr_"DSP|"_chlCnt_"||"_chl_"^^^|||"_cr
		S chlCnt=chlCnt+1
	}
 	I '$L(chlStr) {
	 	W "在检验系统未找到条码:"_labno_"对应的化验项目信息,确定医嘱或项目维护正确?",!    
        Q 1
	}
	S specimenDR=$LG($G(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(visiNumberDR)),56)
	S specimenName=""
	S:$L(specimenDR) specimenName=$LG($G(^dbo.BTSpecimenD(specimenDR)),3)
	S sampleType="其他"
	I $L(specimenName),",血清,血浆,尿液,脑脊液,"[(","_specimenName_",") {
		S sampleType=specimenName
	}
	S birdthday=visNumberObj.BirthDate
	S:$L(birdthday)=8 birdthday=birdthday_"000000"
    S mshSeq=$P(mshStr,"|",10)
    S $P(mshStr,"|",9)="DSR^Q03"
    S mshStr=$P(mshStr,"|",1,2)_"|LIS|||"_$P(mshStr,"|",6,$l(mshStr))
	S order=mshStr_cr //"MSH|^~\&|||||20160122110540||DSR^Q03|14|P|2.3.1||||||ASCII|||"_cr
	S order=order_"MSA|AA|"_mshSeq_"|Message accepted|||0|"_cr
	S order=order_"ERR|0|"_cr
	S order=order_"QAK|SR|OK|"_cr
	S order=order_qrdStr_cr  //"QRD|20160122110540|R|D|1|||RD||OTH|||T|"_cr
	S order=order_qrfStr_cr  //"QRF|iFlash3000|||||RCT|COR|ALL||"_cr
	S order=order_"DSP|1||"_visNumberObj.RegNo_"|||"_cr		//住院号
	S order=order_"DSP|2||"_visNumberObj.BedNo_"|||"_cr		//床号
	S order=order_"DSP|3||"_visNumberObj.SurName_"|||"_cr	//病人姓名
	S order=order_"DSP|4||"_birdthday_"|||"_cr				//出生日期
	S order=order_"DSP|5||"_$S(visNumberObj.SpeciesDR=1:"M",visNumberObj.SpeciesDR=2:"F",1:"O")_"|||"_cr	//性别
	S order=order_"DSP|6|||||"_cr				//血型
	S order=order_"DSP|7|||||"_cr				//种族
	S order=order_"DSP|8|||||"_cr				//地址
	S order=order_"DSP|9|||||"_cr				//邮编
	S order=order_"DSP|10|||||"_cr				//家庭电话
	S order=order_"DSP|11|||||"_cr				//样本位
	S order=order_"DSP|12|||||"_cr				//样本采集时间
	S order=order_"DSP|13|||||"_cr				//未用
	S order=order_"DSP|14|||||"_cr				//未用
	S order=order_"DSP|15|||||"_cr				//病人类别
	S order=order_"DSP|16|||||"_cr				//医保帐号
	S order=order_"DSP|17|||||"_cr				//收费类型
	S order=order_"DSP|18|||||"_cr				//民族
	S order=order_"DSP|19|||||"_cr				//籍贯
	S order=order_"DSP|20|||||"_cr				//国家
	S order=order_"DSP|21||"_barcode_"|||"_cr	//*样本条码
	S order=order_"DSP|22||"_barcode_"|||"_cr	//*样本编号
	S order=order_"DSP|23|||||"_cr				//送检时间
	S order=order_"DSP|24||"_$S(visNumberObj.Urgent=1:"Y",1:"N")_"|||"_cr				//*是否急诊
	S order=order_"DSP|25|||||"_cr				//未用
	S order=order_"DSP|26||"_sampleType_"|||"_cr	//*样本类型(血清,血浆,尿液,脑脊液,其他)
	S order=order_"DSP|27|||||"_cr	//送检医生
	S order=order_"DSP|28|||||"_cr		//送检科室
	S order=order_chlStr
	S order=order_"DSC|"_DSC_"|"_cr
    W sb,order,eb,cr,! 
    Q 0
    
    
TransResult(miRowId,result)
	N (miRowId,result)
	S miRowId=$G(miRowId),result=$G(result),newRes=""
	F i=1:1:$L(result,",") {
		S chlStr=$P(result,",",i)
		Continue:'$L(chlStr)
		S chl=$P(chlStr,"\",1)
		S val=$P(chlStr,"\",2)
		Continue:'$L(chl)
		S res=val
		I chl>97,chl<102,val'["?" {
			S res=$$GetQuaResult(miRowId,chl,val)
		}
		S newRes=newRes_chl_$C(92)_res_$C(44)	
	}
	Q:$L(newRes) newRes
	Q result

GetQuaResult(miRowId,chl,res)
	N (miRowId,chl,res)
	S miRowId=$G(miRowId),chl=$G(chl),res=$G(res)
	S:res?1"."1.N res="0"_res
	S orgRes=res
	S resPrefix=$E(res,1)
	S:"<>"'[resPrefix resPrefix=""
	I $L(resPrefix) {
		S res=$P(res,resPrefix,2)	
	}
	Q:'$L(chl) orgRes
	Q:(res'?0.N1."."1.N)&&(res'?1.N) orgRes
	S tcRefRowId=$O(^dbo.BTMIMachineTestCodeI("IndexResultChannel",miRowId," "_$ZCVT(chl,"U"),"")) 
	Q:'$L(tcRefRowId) orgRes
	S tcRowId=$LG($G(^dbo.BTMIMachineTestCodeD(tcRefRowId)),3)
	Q:'$L(tcRowId) orgRes
	S orderNo=$O(^dbo.BTTestCodeRangesI("IndexMaster",tcRowId,""))
	Q:'$L(orderNo) orgRes
	S rangeDR=$O(^dbo.BTTestCodeRangesI("IndexMaster",tcRowId,orderNo,""))
	Q:'$L(rangeDR) orgRes
	S rangeObj=##Class(dbo.BTTestCodeRanges).%OpenId(rangeDR)
	Q:'$L(rangeObj) orgRes
	
	I res>=rangeObj.ValueHigh {
		I resPrefix="<" {
			Q orgRes
		}
		Q "阳性("_orgRes_")"
	} ELSE {
		I resPrefix=">" {
			Q orgRes
		}
	}
	Q "阴性("_orgRes_")"

MIFMYLA(mi)  
	///仪器名称: 梅里埃MYLA
	///仪器厂商: 梅里埃
	///通信协议: ASTM
	///交互方式: 双向
	///接 口: TCP/IP 
	///编 写 者: WxC
	///编写日期: 2023-08-10
	s mi=$g(mi) 
	s ^TMPMACH10(mi,104)=$H
	i '$l(mi) q
	s ItemDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),12) //项目分隔符
	s ResultDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),13) //结果分隔符
	s AntDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),14) //抗生素分隔符
	s SenDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),15) //药敏结果分隔符
	s Port="|TCP|"_$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),17)  //端口号
	s mi=mi
	//控制字符
	s isDebug=1,iError=100
	s stx=$c(2),etx=$c(3),ack=$c(6),enq=$c(5),eot=$c(4),lf=$c(10),cr=$c(13),nak=$c(21),etb=$c(23),end=$c(30)
	s stx=$c(2),etx=$c(3),ack=$c(6),enq=$c(5),eot=$c(4),etb=$c(23),del="|"
  	s end=$c(30),gs=$c(29),rs=$c(30)
  	s lf=$c(10),cr=$c(13),nak=$c(21),(AllRecord,result,epis)="",kk=1
	S ^TMPMACH10(mi,102)=$H
	i $$StartUTF8^MI.MIF000(mi) q
	f  d Main i $$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi) q
  	c Port
    q
  
Main  
  r *R:10 e  d  q
  .d ORDER
  SET $ZTRAP="ERR" 
  i $c(R)=enq d
  .d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"ENQ","H<--M")
  .d ACK s enqcnt=""
  .f  r *R:10 q:$c(R)=eot  q:R=-1  d
  ..i $c(R)'=stx q
  ..s record=$$Read^MI.MIF000(mi,end,$c(29)) q:'$l(record)
  ..d ACK
  ..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"H<--M")
  ..s record=$tr(record,rs)
  ..s record=$tr(record,cr)
  ..s record=$tr(record,lf)
  ..s AllRecord=record
  ..i $l(record,etb)>1 s AllRecord=AllRecord_$p($e(record,2,$l(record)-1),etb,1)
  ..i $l(record,etx)>1 s AllRecord=AllRecord_$p($e(record,2,$l(record)-1),etx,1)
  ..d Result
  .d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$s($c(R)=eot:"EOT",1:R),"H<--M")
  q
  
ERR
  h 5
  d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$ZERROR_".错误代码:"_$ECODE,"err")
  q 

Result
  s (ORG,xANT,xMIC,xRES,ANTSTR)=""
  s (sample,epis,surname,result,date,time,QC)=""
  s isolate=1
  f k=1:1:$l(AllRecord,"zz") d
  .s recstr=$p(AllRecord,"zz",k)
  .f i=1:1:$l(recstr,del) d
  ..s fldstr=$p(recstr,del,i)
  ..i $e(fldstr,1,2)="ci" d  q   ///epis
  ...s epis=$e(fldstr,3,$l(fldstr))
  ...;i $l(epis)<9 s epis=$tr($j(epis,9)," ","0")
  ..i $e(fldstr,1,2)="t1" d  q  ///isolate NO
  ...s isolate=$e(fldstr,3,$l(fldstr))
  ...i '$l(isolate) s isolate=1
  ..i $e(fldstr,1,2)="o1" d  q  ///org
  ...i $l(ORG) s result=result_ORG_ResultDeli_ANTSTR_ResultDeli_isolate_ItemDeli
  ...s (ORG,xANT,xMIC,xRES,ANTSTR)=""
  ...s ORG=$e(fldstr,3,$l(fldstr))
  ..i $e(fldstr,1,2)="a1" d  q  ///ant
  ...s xANT=$e(fldstr,3,$l(fldstr))
  ..i $e(fldstr,1,2)="a3" d  q  ///mic
  ...s xMIC=$e(fldstr,3,$l(fldstr))
  ..i $e(fldstr,1,2)="a4" d  q  ///res
  ...s xRES=$e(fldstr,3,$l(fldstr))
  ...i $l(xANT),$l(xRES) D
  ....S xMIC=$TR(xMIC," ")
  ....i xMIC="SYN-R" s xMIC=""
  ....i xMIC="SYN-S" s xMIC=""
  ....I xANT="HLG",'$L(xMIC) D  //高浓度庆大霉素,wwh,20150708
  .....S:xRES="R" xMIC=">500"
  .....S:xRES="S" xMIC="<500"
  ....I xANT="HLS",'$L(xMIC) D	//高浓度链霉素,wwh,20150708
  .....S:xRES="R" xMIC=">1000"
  .....S:xRES="S" xMIC="<=500"
  ....I xANT="SXT" D	//复方新诺明,wwh,20150708
  .....//转换结果 20160126 huhm
  .....s Flag="",MicRes=xMIC

  .....i $e(MicRes,1)="=" s Flag=Flag_$e(MicRes,1),MicRes=$e(MicRes,2,$l(MicRes))
  .....S:MicRes="10" MicRes="0.5/9.5"
  .....S:MicRes="20" MicRes="1/19"
  .....S:MicRes="40" MicRes="2/38"
  .....S:MicRes="80" MicRes="4/76"

  ....s (xANT,xMIC,xRES)=""
  .i $l(ORG) s result=result_ORG_ResultDeli_ANTSTR_ResultDeli_isolate_ItemDeli
  .d Last
  q
  
Last  ; file result if exist

  .d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"$$"_result,"Result")

ACK  ; send 'ack' to instrument

特殊功能

批量保存通道号

由于微生物细菌和抗生素通道号较多，编写此方法批量导入

/dthealth/app/dthis/imedicallis/imedicallis/tmp/File

IsSave参数，可以先进行查看，查看查询数和匹配数，确认后再进行保存，避免出错

ClassMethod fileMTHD(mi, record, epis, P3, P4, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %String
{
  s mi=$g(mi)
  s epis=$g(epis)
  i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q
  i '$l(record) q
  s (epis,code,res,result,date,time,QC)=""
  s (type,AntFlag,Ant,AntM,AntR,Bacteria,episF,recorda,recordb)=""
  s (xBug,xBugs,AntLIST,xANT,xRES,xMIC,xMM,AntGroup,xMICF,fresult)=""
  s (fresult,date,time,QC,AntLIST)=""
  s type=$p(record,"|",1)
  s record=$TR(record," """)
  s record=$replace(record,"[13][10]",",")
  d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"H<--M")
  s MachType=$P($P(record,"<testGroupCode>",2),"</testGroupCode>",1)   //BC SU
  s epis=$P($P(record,"<specimenIdentifier>",2),"</specimenIdentifier>",1)
  

  i MachType["ID" d		  //质谱结果
  .s (xbug,isolateNumber,ret,Bugsresult)=""
  .s code=$P($P(record,"<isolateNumber>",2),"</isolateNumber>",1)
  .i record["<significantTaxon>" d
  ..s str=$P(record,"<significantTaxon>",2)
  ..s xbug=$P($P(str,"<code>",2),"</code>",1)
  .i record["<probability>" d 
  ..s percent=$p($P(record,"<probability>",2),"</probability>",1)
  .i record["<isolateNumber>" d
  ..s isolateNumber=$p($P(record,"<isolateNumber>",2),"</isolateNumber>",1)
  .;i $l(xbug),$l(percent) s res="质谱结果:"_xbug_" "_percent
  .;i $l(res) s result="ZPJG"_$c(92)_res_$c(44)

/// Query的执行方法
/// d ##class(%ResultSet).RunQuery("MI.MIFBACK3D","QryLabInfo","72","","","","","","","","","","","","","","","")
ClassMethod QryLabInfoExecute(ByRef qHandle As %Binary, mi As %String, P1, P2, P3, P4, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %Status
{
	Set repid=$i(^CacheTemp)
    Set ind=1
    s mi=$g(mi),flag=$g(flag)
    i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q ""
    s LabnoList=""
    s AddDate="" f  s AddDate=$o(^dbo.RPMachineUploadI("IndexSendStatus",mi,"C",AddDate)) q:AddDate=""  d
    .s AddTime="" f  s AddTime=$o(^dbo.RPMachineUploadI("IndexSendStatus",mi,"C",AddDate,AddTime)) q:AddTime=""  d
    ..s MiUploadDR=$o(^dbo.RPMachineUploadI("IndexSendStatus",mi,"C",AddDate,AddTime,""))
    ..s labno=$lg(^dbo.RPMachineUploadD(MiUploadDR),3)
    ..s LabnoOld=labno
    ..i '$l(labno) q
    ..b ;ch1
    ..s labnoInfo=..GetLabnoInfo(mi,labno)
    ..s labnoInfo2=..GetLabnoInfoR(mi,labno)
    ..s patInfo=..GetPatInfo(mi,labno)
    ..s Name="lis_"_$TR($ZD($H,3),"-")_"_"_$TR($p($ZDT($H)," ",2),":")_"_1"_".xml"
    ..s Name2="lis_"_$TR($ZD($H,3),"-")_"_"_$TR($p($ZDT($H)," ",2),":")_"_2"_".xml"

    ..s Data=##class(MI.Common.MIFBase).DemoMOutFileInfo(Name,labnoInfo,labno,"","$Encoding.UTF8")
    ..d OutputRow
    ..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,LabnoOld_"$$"_Name2_"$$"_labnoInfo2,"上传信息2")
    ..s Data=##class(MI.Common.MIFBase).DemoMOutFileInfo(Name2,labnoInfo2,LabnoOld,"","$Encoding.UTF8")
    ..d OutputRow
    Set qHandle=$lb(0,repid,0)
    Quit $$$OK
   
    
    
OutputRow
    ;Set Data=$lb(flabno,labnoInfo,patInfo)
    Set ColFields="labno,labnoInfo,patInfo"
    Set ^CacheTemp(repid,ind)=##Class(LIS.Util.Common).TransListNull(Data,ColFields)
    Set ind=ind+1
    quit
}

ClassMethod QryLabInfoClose(ByRef qHandle As %Binary) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Kill ^CacheTemp(repid)
    Quit $$$OK
}

ClassMethod QryLabInfoFetch(ByRef qHandle As %Binary, ByRef Row As %List, ByRef AtEnd As %Integer = 0) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set AtEnd=$LIST(qHandle,1)
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Set ind=$LIST(qHandle,3)
    Set ind=$o(^CacheTemp(repid,ind))
    If ind="" { 
        Set AtEnd=1
        Set Row=""
    }
    Else      { 
        Set Row=^CacheTemp(repid,ind)
    }
    // Save QHandle
    s qHandle=$lb(AtEnd,repid,ind)
    Quit $$$OK
}

Change(mi,epis,code,res)

	s res1=""

	s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR,21,OrderNO,""))

GetEpisByLabno(mi,Epis)
	//通过检验号获取流水号
	;Index IndexVisitNumber On VisitNumber [ SqlName = Index_VisitNumber, Type = index, Unique ];
	;Index IndexReportID On (VisitNumberDR, WorkGroupMachineDR, OrderNo) [ SqlName = Index_ReportID, Type = index, Unique ];
	s GetEpisFlag=0		//获取最后一个 0 ，获取所有的 1
	s ret="",mi=$g(mi),Epis=$g(Epis)
	i '$l(mi) q Epis
	s WGMachineID=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6)
	i GetEpisFlag=0 d

	...s ret=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(ReportDR)),8)
	i GetEpisFlag=1 d
	.i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",Epis)) d
	..s VisitnumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",Epis,""))
	..s OrderNo="" f  s OrderNo=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitnumberDR,WGMachineID,OrderNo)) q:OrderNo=""  d
	...s ReportDR="" f  s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitnumberDR,WGMachineID,OrderNo,ReportDR)) q:ReportDR=""  d
